/p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet, Champfleury.&nbsp;Les chats, 1868 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/btv1b9016166j.item\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet,&nbsp;En bateau, 1874 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.metmuseum.org/art/collection/search/436947\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet,&nbsp;Le Buveur d\'absinthe, 1859 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.glyptoteket.dk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet,&nbsp;Le vieux Musicien,&nbsp;1862 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nga.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet,&nbsp;Lola de Valence, 1862 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?no_cache=1&amp;zoom=1&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bzoom%5D=0&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5BxmlId%5D=000710&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bback%5D=%2Ffr%2Fcollections%2Fcatalogue-des-oeuvres%2Fnotice.html%3Fno_cache%3D1%26zsz%3D5%26lnum%3D%26nnumid%3D710\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet,&nbsp;Philosophe assis, c.1860</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet,&nbsp;Le Chanteur espagnol, 1860 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.metmuseum.org/art/collection/search/436944\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet,&nbsp;Victorine Meurent en costume d&rsquo;espada, 1862 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.metmuseum.org/art/collection/search/436945\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;pandage des eaux d&rsquo;&eacute;gouts, &agrave; Gennevilliers, photographie</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Pirou,&nbsp;Portrait d\'Eug&egrave;ne-Ren&eacute; Poubelle</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix Thorigny,&nbsp;Embellissements de Paris. Transformation de la montagne Sainte-Genevi&egrave;ve. Vue prise de la rue Saint-Victor,&nbsp;1866</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix Thorigny, Henry Linton,&nbsp;Percement du Boulevard S&eacute;bastopol ; aspect des d&eacute;molitions de la rue de la Barillerie,&nbsp;1859</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Franck,&nbsp;&Eacute;douard Manet,&nbsp;c.1862</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Fran&ccedil;ois Bonvin,&nbsp;Chiffonnier, 1854</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Fran&ccedil;ois Georgin, Le Juif-errant,&nbsp;c. 1725</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat,&nbsp;Acad&eacute;mie d&rsquo;homme, vu de dos, s&rsquo;appuyant sur b&acirc;ton, 1877</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat,&nbsp;Baignade &agrave; Asni&egrave;res,&nbsp;1884 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nationalgallery.org.uk/paintings/georges-seurat-bathers-at-asnieres\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat,&nbsp;&Eacute;tude pour Une Baignade &agrave; Asni&egrave;res,&nbsp;1883-1884 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?no_cache=1&amp;zoom=1&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bzoom%5D=0&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5BxmlId%5D=000544&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bback%5D=%2Ffr%2Fcollections%2Fcatalogue-des-oeuvres%2Fnotice.html%3Fnnumid%3D544\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat,&nbsp;Les Terrassiers,&nbsp;c.1883 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nga.gov/global-site-search-page.html?searchterm=seurat&amp;category=Works%20of%20Art&amp;pageNumber=1&amp;lastFacet=category\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat,&nbsp;Parade du cirque,&nbsp;1887-1888 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.metmuseum.org/art/collection/search/437654\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat,&nbsp;Paysage avec &laquo;Le pauvre P&ecirc;cheur &raquo; de Puvis de Chavannes, c.1881 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;