veur),&nbsp;Les Plaisirs champ&ecirc;tres du parc du V&eacute;sinet, 1855</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Dor&eacute; (dessin), Ehrard (graveur),&nbsp;L&rsquo;Arbre de Robinson, 1855</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Le Gray,&nbsp;Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Buisson,&nbsp;1848</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse-Lautrec,&nbsp;Jane Avril dansant, 1893 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/works-in-focus/painting/commentaire_id/jane-avril-dancing-8969.html?cHash=8fc9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a>&nbsp;</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri Guillaume Schlesinger,&nbsp;L&acute;Enfant vol&eacute;, 1861</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henry Meyer, Les Camps-Volants. Recensement des boh&eacute;miens en France, dans Le Petit Journal. Suppl&eacute;ment Illustr&eacute;, 5 mai 1895</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Honor&eacute; Daumier, Actualit&eacute;s. On a raison d&rsquo;laisser c&rsquo;te tour l&agrave; debout&hellip;faudrait monter en ballon pour la d&eacute;molir !, lithographie, 20x25,6cm, publi&eacute; dans&nbsp;Le Charivari, 7 d&eacute;cembre 1852</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Honor&eacute; Daumier, Locataires et propri&eacute;taires. Vue prise dans un cartier en d&eacute;molition, 1854</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Hyppolyte-Louis-&Eacute;mile Pauquet, &Eacute;tienne Guillaumot,&nbsp;La B&eacute;arnaise, 1825-1828</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jacques-Louis David,&nbsp;Le Serment des Horaces, 1784-1785 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.louvre.fr/oeuvre-notices/le-serment-des-horaces\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Auguste-Dominique Ingres,&nbsp;La Baigneuse de Valpin&ccedil;on,&nbsp;1808 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.louvre.fr/oeuvre-notices/la-baigneuse\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a>&nbsp;</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">La Grenouill&egrave;re durant la Belle-&Eacute;poque, Mus&eacute;e de la Grenouilli&egrave;re, Croissy-sur-Seine</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">La Maison dor&eacute;e : 20, Boulevard des Italiens, Paris</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Bois de Boulogne. Le lac, les cygnes et les canards &agrave; la Belle &Eacute;poque</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Boulevard des Italiens, c. 1875, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Caravage,&nbsp;Saint Jean Baptiste dans le d&eacute;sert,&nbsp;c.1610 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nelson-atkins.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a>&nbsp;</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">L&eacute;onard de Vinci,&nbsp;L&rsquo;Adoration des mages,&nbsp;c. 1481 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.uffizi.it/opere/adorazione-dei-magi-44ad4c9a-c0bd-432d-8a0c-9807e05055bb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Levallois-Perret. &Icirc;le de la Grande Jatte, c.1900, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Louis-Joseph Anthonissen,&nbsp;Atelier de repasseuses &agrave; Trouville, 1888 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.pau.fr/209-musee-des-beaux-arts.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Louis-Paul-Pierre Dumont, Le Canal Saint-Martin. Vue de la voute souterraine,&nbsp;1862</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Maison Salubre. Tout &agrave; l&rsquo;&Eacute;gout &raquo;, plaque &eacute;maill&eacute;e au 9 rue Beautreillis</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Maison Salubre. Tout &agrave; l&rsquo;&eacute;gout &raquo;, plaque sur le mur du 38, rue du Vertbois</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Map of Paris and its western environs in the late nineteenth century, plate 91, dans Francis Frascina et al.,1993</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Marcelin (dir.), La Vie parisienne : m&oelig;urs &eacute;l&eacute;gantes, choses du jour, fantaisies, voyages, th&eacute;&acirc;tres, musique, modes, couverture, d&eacute;tail, n&ordm;1, 1863</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Maurice de Vlaminck, La Maison bleue, 1906</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Couverture de Michel Eug&egrave;ne Chevreuil,&nbsp;De la loi du contraste simultan&eacute; des couleurs et de l&rsquo;assortiment des objets color&eacute;s, 1839</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Michel Eug&egrave;ne Chevreul, Premier cercle chromatique de M. Chevreuil renfermant les couleurs franches, 1839, dans Michel Eug&egrave;ne Chevreuil,&nbsp;De la loi du contraste simultan&eacute; des couleurs et de l&rsquo;assortiment des objets color&eacute;s, Paris, 1839</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Miranda (dessin), Moller (graveur),&nbsp;Le Sport nautique, mai 1873</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Nadar,&nbsp;Champfleury, c.1860</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Nadar,&nbsp;Edmond et Jules Goncourt, 1854</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Nicolas Poussin,&nbsp;Coriolan suppli&eacute; par sa famille, 1652 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://museenicolaspoussin.fr/index.php/collections/coriolan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pablo Picasso,&nbsp;L&rsquo;Usine, Horta de Ebro, 1909 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://saint-petersbourg.org/ermitage/art-fran%C3%A7ais/pablo-picasso/usine-au-village-horta-de-ebro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paris 17e arrondissement, Rue des Batignolles, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paris. Avenue Rapp. Les Voiture de livraisons dans la Cour des d&eacute;pendances, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paris. Boulevard des Capucines, 9&egrave;me arrondissement, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paris. Caserne du Ch&acirc;teau d&rsquo;Eau, 1902, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paris. Gare Saint-Lazare, c.1900, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paris. Grands Magasins du Louvre. Hall des soieries, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paris. La Caserne de la Cit&eacute;, carte postale&nbsp;</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paris. Voiture de livraisons des Grands Magasins du Louvre, carte postale&nbsp;</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul C&eacute;zanne,&nbsp;Carri&egrave;re &agrave; Bib&eacute;mus,&nbsp;1898-1900 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.museum-folkwang.de/fr/bienvenue.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Destez (dessin), Adolphe Gusman (graveur),&nbsp;L&rsquo;Univers Illustr&eacute;.&nbsp;Le bal du Jeudi soir &agrave; &laquo; La Grenouill&egrave;re &raquo;, 1885</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin,&nbsp;Femmes de Tahiti,&nbsp;1891 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/oeuvres-commentees/recherche/commentaire/commentaire_id/femmes-de-tahiti-16337.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul G&eacute;niaux,&nbsp;Chiffonniers, Paris, 1895-1905 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.carnavalet.paris.fr/fr/collections/photographies\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Hadol,&nbsp;Le Salon comique,&nbsp;1875</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Sescau,&nbsp;Jane Avril, c.1890</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pavillon de la Ville de Paris, Salon d&rsquo;Hiver de la Soci&eacute;t&eacute; des Artistes Ind&eacute;pendants, 1884-1885</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Philippe Jacques Potteau, Jean Lagr&egrave;ne (66 ans), 1865</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Piero della Francesca,&nbsp;La Vision de Constantin, 1452-1466 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.museistataliarezzo.it/en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Piero della Francesca,&nbsp;La R&eacute;surrection,&nbsp;c.1460 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.museocivicosansepolcro.it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pierre Puvis de Chavannes,&nbsp;Le Bois sacr&eacute; cher aux arts et aux muses, 1884 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.mba-lyon.fr/mba/sections/fr/collections-musee/peintures/oeuvres-peintures/xixe_siecle/le_bois_sacre_cher_a/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pierre Puvis de Chavannes,&nbsp;Le pauvre P&ecirc;cheur,&nbsp;1881 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/index.php?id=851&amp;L=0&amp;tx_commentaire_pi1%5BshowUid%5D=373\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pierre Puvis de Chavannes,&nbsp;Marseille colonie grecque,&nbsp;1869 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://culture.marseille.fr/les-musees-de-marseille/le-musee-des-beaux-arts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Poubelles et voiture hippomobile propos&eacute;es en mod&egrave;le pour Angers par L&rsquo;Ouest, &laquo; Pour qu&rsquo;Angers soit propre &raquo;, 20 et 21 octobre 1912</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Provost, Paris nouveau.&nbsp;Vue d&rsquo;une partie de la rue de Rivoli dans son &eacute;tat actuel, prise du coin de la place du Palais Royal</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Puteaux. L&rsquo;&Iacute;&Icirc;e d&rsquo;Amour (Vue Int&eacute;rieure). Le Temple de l&rsquo;Amour, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Rapha&euml;l,&nbsp;L&acute;&Eacute;cole d&acute;Ath&egrave;nes, 1509-1510 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.museivaticani.va/content/museivaticani/fr/musei-del-papa.html#lnav_info\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a>&nbsp;</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Robert Doisneau,&nbsp;Structure m&eacute;tallique pavillon Baltard</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Rue de Rivoli, le long du jardin des Tuileries, c.1890, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Roger-Joseph Jourdain,&nbsp;Dimanche &agrave; la Grande Jatte, 1878 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.petitpalais.paris.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Roger-Joseph Jourdain,&nbsp;Le Lundi (Monday, men around table in park drinking wine, from painting),&nbsp;c.1878</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Rue Mouffetard, Un dimanche matin, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Sc&egrave;nes Parisiennes.&nbsp;Chiffonni&egrave;res, 1910, carte postale</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Thomas Couture,&nbsp;Les Romains de la d&eacute;cadence, 1847 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/oeuvres-commentees/peinture/commentaire_id/romains-de-la-decadence-141.html?cHash=f2db32e74a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Thomas Couture,&nbsp;Portrait d&rsquo;Antoine &Eacute;tex, 1845-1855</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Thomas Couture,&nbsp;Autoportrait, c.1840 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.wikiart.org/en/thomas-couture/self-portrait\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Trock, Ces bons Parisiens, 1882</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vassily Kandinsky,&nbsp;&Eacute;tude de couleurs, carr&eacute;s avec cercles concentriques, c.1913 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.lenbachhaus.de/das-museum/das-lenbachhaus/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent Van Gogh,&nbsp;La Nuit &eacute;toil&eacute;e, 1889 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.moma.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent Van Gogh,&nbsp;Laboureur dans un champ pr&egrave;s d\'Arles, 1888 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.vangoghgallery.com/catalog/Drawing/1394/Ploughman-in-the-Fields-near-Arles.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `videosonline` (`id`, `title_fr`, `subtitle_fr`, `text_fr`, `texto_secondary_fr`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `image`, `color`, `home_image`, `title`, `subtitle`, `text`, `texto_secondary`, `bio`, `ilustraciones`, `order`) VALUES
(7, 'Olympia et Un bar aux Folies Bergère', 'Deux chefs-d\'œuvre d\'Édouard Manet', '<p>Olympia et Un bar aux Folies Berg&egrave;re&nbsp;d\'&Eacute;douard Manet sont des toiles si famili&egrave;res qu\'elles en auraient presque perdu leur myst&egrave;re. Qu\'en est-il d\'Olympia&nbsp;? Pourquoi ce qui n\'&eacute;tait finalement qu\'un nu parmi tant d\'autres devait d&eacute;clencher le toll&eacute; le plus virulent que Paris, capitale de la prostitution, ait alors connu ? Histoire d\'un triple tabou, philosophique, bourgeois et sexuel.</p>\r\n<p>Quant au Bar, qui est cette jeune femme luxueusement v&ecirc;tue mais occupant la fonction de serveuse aux Folies Berg&egrave;re ? Comment se situe-t-elle par rapport au spectateur ? au client ? Le saura-t-on jamais ? La richesse du tableau r&eacute;side aussi dans la multitude des interpr&eacute;tations possibles.</p>\r\n<p>Ces deux chefs-d\'&oelig;uvre de l\'art occidental fascinent ; Manet ne cesse aujourd\'hui encore de surprendre. Hommage au ma&icirc;tre.</p>', 'Avec Olympia et Un bar aux Folies Bergère, Édouard Manet essuie son second et dernier lynchage médiatique.', '2024-10-11 23:00:00', '2024-11-09 02:02:18', 'videosonline/October2024/YoJQb4cphj7cx2VmLISn.jpg', '#bb2217', 'videosonline/October2024/uBDA3IBdH7UxfCj7hRzI.jpg', 'Olympia and a bar at the Folies Bergère', 'Two masterpieces by Édouard Manet', '<p>Olympia and A Bar at the Folies Berg&egrave;re by &Eacute;douard Manet are such familiar paintings that they have almost lost their mystery. What about Olympia? Why did what was ultimately just another nude among many others trigger the most virulent outcry that Paris, the capital of prostitution, had ever known? The story of a triple taboo: philosophical, bourgeois and sexual.</p>\r\n<p>As for The Bar, who is this luxuriously dressed young woman working as a waitress at the Folies Berg&egrave;re? How does she relate to the viewer? to the customer? Will we ever know? The richness of the painting also lies in the multitude of possible interpretations.</p>\r\n<p>These two masterpieces of Western art fascinate; Manet continues to surprise us today. Homage to the master.</p>', 'With Olympia and Un bar aux Folies Bergère, Édouard Manet suffered his second and final media lynching.', '<p><em>Splendeurs et mis&egrave;res : image de la prostitution</em>, 1850-1910, Orsay, Flammarion, 2016</p>\r\n<p>Julia Kristeva, <em>Visions capitales</em>, Fayard, 2013.</p>\r\n<p>Timothy James Clark,<em> Image of the People &ndash; Gustave Courbet and the 1848 Revolution</em>, Thames and Hudson, 1973</p>\r\n<p>Bradford R. Collins ed., <em>Twelve Views of Manet\'s Bar</em>, . Princeton Series in 19th Century Art, 1996</p>\r\n<p>Michel Foucault, <em>La Peinture de Manet, Conf&eacute;rence &agrave; Tunis</em>, 20 Mai 1971</p>', '<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet,&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Olympia</span>, 1863-1865 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/en/collections/works-in-focus/search/commentaire_id/olympia-7087.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Joseph Dantan, &nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Un coin du Salon en 1880</span>, 1880<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Bertall,&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Manette ou La femme de l&acute;&eacute;b&eacute;niste</span>, publi&eacute; dans Journal Amusant du 27 mai 1865<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Titien, Venus d&acute;Urbin (Venere di Urbino), 1538 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.uffizi.it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, V&eacute;nus d\'Urbin, copie d\'apr&egrave;s le tableau de Titien, 1856<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Giorgione et Titien, Venus endormie (Venere dormiente), c.1510 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://gemaeldegalerie.skd.museum/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Rembrandt van Rijn, Bethsab&eacute;e au bain tenant la lettre de David, 1654 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.louvre.fr/oeuvre-notices/bethsabee-au-bain-tenant-la-lettre-de-david\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Charles Gleyre, Coucher de Sapho, 1867 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;</span><a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.mcba.ch/en/collection/artists/oeuvres-commentees-art-ancien-et-moderne/gleyre-sapho/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">ici</span></a><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Alphonse Lecadre, Nu allong&eacute;, 1870<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Auguste-Dominique Ingres, Venus anadyom&egrave;ne, 1808-1848 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.musee-conde.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Adolphe Bouguereau, La Naissance de V&eacute;nus, 1879 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/resultat-collection.html?no_cache=1&amp;zoom=1&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bzoom%5D=0&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5BxmlId%5D=016649&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bback%5D=fr%2Fcollections%2Fcatalogue-des-oeuvres%2Fresultat-collection.html%3Fno_cache%3D1%26zsz%3D9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Alexandre Cabanel, Nymphe enlev&eacute;e par un faune, 1860 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?no_cache=1&amp;zoom=1&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bzoom%5D=0&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5BxmlId%5D=069684&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bback%5D=%2Ffr%2Fcollections%2Fcatalogue-des-oeuvres%2Fnotice.html%3Fnnumid%3D69684\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Alexandre Cabanel, La Naissance de V&eacute;nus, 1863 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?no_cache=1&amp;zoom=1&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bzoom%5D=0&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5BxmlId%5D=000098&amp;tx_damzoom_pi1%5Bback%5D=%2Ffr%2Fcollections%2Fcatalogue-des-oeuvres%2Fnotice.html%3Fno_cache%3D1%26zsz%3D5%26lnum%3D%26nnumid%3D98\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Baudry, La perle et la vague, 1862<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Fran&ccedil;ois L&eacute;on B&eacute;nouville, Esther ou Odalisque, 1844 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.pau.fr/209-musee-des-beaux-arts.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Auguste-Dominique Ingres, Odalisque &agrave; l\'esclave, 1839 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.louvre.fr/oeuvre-notices/l-odalisque-l-esclave\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Auguste-Dominique Ingres, La Grande Odalisque, 1814 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;</span><a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.louvre.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">ici</span></a><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-L&eacute;on G&eacute;r&ocirc;me, L\'int&eacute;rieur grec, Le gyn&eacute;c&eacute;e, 1850<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-L&eacute;on G&eacute;r&ocirc;me, Phryn&eacute; devant l\'Ar&eacute;opage, 1861 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.hamburger-kunsthalle.de/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Honor&eacute; Daumier, Croquis pris au Salon, 1865<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Registre des condamnations pour m&oelig;urs Augustine Guy dite D&eacute;bureau vers 1861<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix-Jacques Moulin, Nu allong&eacute; souriant, 1852 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?nnumid=068703\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix-Jacques Moulin, Nu assis, daguerr&eacute;otype st&eacute;r&eacute;oscopique, d&eacute;tail, 1852<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse-Lautrec, La visite m&eacute;dicale, c.1894 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://musees-occitanie.fr/encyclopedie/themes/arts-graphiques/toulouse-lautrec-et-les-maisons-closes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean B&eacute;raud, La salle des filles au d&eacute;p&ocirc;t, 1886<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse-Lautrec, Salon de la rue des Moulins, 1894-1895 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://musees-occitanie.fr/musees/musee-toulouse-lautrec/collections/la-collection-toulouse-lautrec/henri-de-toulouse-lautrec/au-salon-de-la-rue-des-moulins-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse-Lautrec, Au Moulin-Rouge, 1892 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.artic.edu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse-Lautrec, La Goulue, 1891 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://discovernewfields.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pascal Dagnan-Bouveret, La blanchisseuse ou Sur les quais de Paris en automne,1880<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pascal Dagnan-Bouveret, La blanchisseuse, 1879<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">James Tissot, La demoiselle de magasin, 1883-1885 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://ago.ca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pierre-Auguste Renoir, Les parapluies, 1883 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nationalgallery.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">James Tissot, La demoiselle d\'honneur ou Voyageurs, 1883/85<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean B&eacute;raud, L\'attente, c.1885 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?nnumid=016606\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean B&eacute;raud, La proposition, rue Chateaubriand, 1885/1890 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean B&eacute;raud, Sur le boulevard, c.1885 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.carnavalet.paris.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean B&eacute;raud, Le boulevard des Capucines, devant le th&eacute;&acirc;tre du Vaudeville, 1889 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.carnavalet.paris.fr/fr/collections/le-boulevard-des-capucines-devant-le-theatre-du-vaudeville\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Giovanni Boldini, Traversant la rue, 1873/75<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean B&eacute;raud, La Modiste sur les Champs Elys&eacute;es, c.1885<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean B&eacute;raud, Champs-Elys&eacute;es, c.1885<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Louis Forain, Au jardin de Paris, 1884<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, Nana, 1877 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.hamburger-kunsthalle.de/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">James Tissot, La Mondaine, 1883/85<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">James Tissot, Evening, 1878 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/oeuvres-commentees/peinture/commentaire_id/evening-21061.html?cHash=23a5be6aea\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">James Tissot, L\'ambitieuse, 1883/85 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.albrightknox.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Amaury Duval, Naissance de V&eacute;nus, 1862 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.pba-lille.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Auguste-Dominique Ingres, La Baigneuse Valpin&ccedil;on, 1808 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.louvre.fr/oeuvre-notices/la-baigneuse\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Giacito Calandrucci, T&ecirc;te de M&eacute;duse, XVIIe si&egrave;cle<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Caravage, M&eacute;duse Murtola, c.1597<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Cham, La naissance du petit &eacute;beniste, publi&eacute; dans Le Charivari du 14 mai 1865<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, Un Bar aux Folies Berg&egrave;re, 1881-1882 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://courtauld.ac.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Charles Fichot, Le grand escalier du Bon March&eacute;, rue de S&egrave;vres, &agrave; Paris, 1872<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, Au caf&eacute;, 1878 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://thewalters.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean B&eacute;raud, La brasserie, 1882<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Giovanni Boldini, Sc&egrave;ne de f&ecirc;te, c.1889 ; lien vers le mus&eacute;e ici<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, La serveuse de bocks, 1878-79 ;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/accueil.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Josef Engelhart, Loge dans la Sofiensal, (loge in Sofiensal) 1903<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Photographie des Folies Berg&egrave;re<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">G. Lafosse, Aux Folies Berg&egrave;re, Publi&eacute; dans Le Journal Amusant du 14 d&eacute;cembre 1878<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Au Bar anglo-am&eacute;ricain George Augustus Henry Sala , Paris herself Again vol1 1878-1879 JE<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jules Ch&eacute;ret, Affiche publicitaire pour les Folies-Berg&egrave;re, 1875<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Stop, Une marchande de consolation aux Folies Berg&egrave;re, publi&eacute; dans Le Journal Amusant, 27 mai 1882<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, &Eacute;tude pour Un Bar aux Folies Berg&egrave;re, c.1881<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Louis-Henry Dupray, Autoportrait, lavis, dans AM Belina Nos peintres dessin&eacute;s par eux-m&ecirc;mes, Paris, 1883<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, Un bar aux Folies Berg&egrave;re, rayon X, 1934<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Catherine Labour&eacute; Novice des S&oelig;urs de la Charit&eacute;<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Statuette de la vierge, 19e<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jules Laurens d&acute;apr&egrave;s Jean-Hippolyte Flandrin, Mater Dolorosa ou M&egrave;re des douleurs, 1845<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, L\'Immacul&eacute;e conception, de la tr&egrave;s sainte Vierge, 1836<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">P&eacute;pin, Vie de Veuillot immacul&eacute;, publi&eacute; dans Les petites &oelig;uvres choisies de L&eacute;o Taxi, 1884<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Frid&acute;rick, La Nouvelle Vierge, Calotte et Calotins, publi&eacute; dans Les petites &oelig;uvres de L&eacute;o Taxi, 1879<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Piero della Francesca, La r&eacute;surrection, 1463-65 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.museocivicosansepolcro.it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, Une botte d\'asperges, 1880 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.wallraf.museum/ausstellungen/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, L\'asperge, 1880 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/index.php?id=851&amp;L=1&amp;tx_commentaire_pi1%5BshowUid%5D=18315\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, Bouquet de violettes, 1872<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, Coin de caf&eacute;-concert, 1879 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nationalgallery.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edouard Manet, Le chemin de fer, 1872-1873 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nga.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix Nadar, &Eacute;douard Manet, 1874 ;&nbsp;<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.bridgemanimages.com/fr/asset/164227/nadar-gaspard-felix-tournachon-1820-1910/portrait-of-edouard-manet-1874-b-w-photo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ici</a></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `videosonline` (`id`, `title_fr`, `subtitle_fr`, `text_fr`, `texto_secondary_fr`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `image`, `color`, `home_image`, `title`, `subtitle`, `text`, `texto_secondary`, `bio`, `ilustraciones`, `order`) VALUES
(8, 'La Saga impressionniste', 'Célèbres et admirés, déconstruction d’un mythe', '<p>Le terme &laquo; impressionnisme &raquo;&nbsp;renvoie-t-il &agrave; une &eacute;cole clairement d&eacute;finie ? Dans ce but, interrogeons point par point nos certitudes. Le mouvement serait n&eacute; d\'un vaste scandale cher aux gen&egrave;ses modernistes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;L\'impressionnisme serait-il une &eacute;cole ? Qui en serait alors le ma&icirc;tre, les disciples ? L\'impressionnisme se distinguerait-il par un style propre ? Encore faudrait-il justifier &acute;une coh&eacute;rence stylistique entre Claude Monet et Edgar Degas. Un sujet de pr&eacute;dilection commun ? Quand les uns optent pour le paysage intemporel tandis que les autres croquent les figures de la vie moderne, la g&eacute;n&eacute;ralisation est trompeuse.</p>\r\n<p>Cette conf&eacute;rence reviendra sur certains pr&eacute;jug&eacute;s, abordant l\'impressionnisme &agrave; l\'aune de sa pluralit&eacute;. Apprendre &agrave; regarder les tableaux les plus connus sans admettre le convenu de l\'histoire.</p>', 'Le discours officiel sur les impressionnistes promeut une étiquette marchandisable et une conception simplificatrice du groupe.', '2024-10-11 23:04:00', '2024-11-09 01:55:39', 'videosonline/October2024/ZcmuFLommmctALaBiLT7.jpg', '#acddf8', 'videosonline/October2024/T2Dx7YxNhITSqI6MNQan.jpg', 'The Impressionist Saga', 'Famous and admired, deconstruction of a myth', '<p>Does the term \"impressionism\" refer to a clearly defined school? To this end, let us question our certainties point by point. The movement would have been born from a vast scandal dear to the modernist geneses.</p>\r\n<p>Is impressionism a school? Who would then be its master, the disciples? Would impressionism be distinguished by its own style? It would still be necessary to justify a stylistic coherence between Claude Monet and Edgar Degas. A common favorite subject? When some opt for the timeless landscape while others sketch the figures of modern life, the generalization is misleading.</p>\r\n<p>This conference will return to certain prejudices, approaching impressionism in the light of its plurality. Learn to look at the most famous paintings without admitting the conventionality of history.</p>', 'The official discourse on the Impressionists promotes a commodifiable label and a simplistic conception of the group.', '<p>John Rewald, <em>The History of Impressionism</em>, Museum of Modern Art, 1973</p>\r\n<p>Richard R. Bretell,<em> Impression, Painting Quickly in France</em>, 1860-1890, Yale UP., 2000</p>', '<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri Fantin-Latour,&nbsp;Hommage &agrave; Delacroix,&nbsp;1864 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/en/collections/works-in-focus/painting/commentaire_id/homage-to-delacroix-2952.html?cHash=b019618a5a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a>&nbsp;</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix,&nbsp;La Mort de Sardanapale, 1827 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.philamuseum.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix ,&nbsp;La Chasse aux lions, esquisse, c.1854 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/oeuvres-commentees/recherche/commentaire/commentaire_id/chasse-aux-lions-191.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anthea Callen, Palette probable de Manet, pour&nbsp;Paveurs, rue de Berne, 1878</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;Palette de l&rsquo;artiste, 1966</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix,&nbsp;Cul de four, 1840-1846 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.assemblee-nationale.fr/histoire/7gaa.asp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, La Mer vue des hauteurs de Dieppe, 1852 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.louvre.fr/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;Bateaux au port de Honfleur,&nbsp;1866</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pierre-Auguste Renoir,&nbsp;Diane La Chasseresse, 1867 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nga.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet,&nbsp;Le Chasseur allemand, 1859</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pierre-Auguste Renoir,&nbsp;La Baigneuse au griffon, 1870 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://masp.org.br/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Les Baigneuses, 1853 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://museefabre.montpellier3m.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Les Demoiselles des bords de Seine (&eacute;t&eacute;),&nbsp;1857 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.petitpalais.paris.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet,&nbsp;L&rsquo;Apr&egrave;s-d&icirc;n&eacute;e &agrave; Ornans,&nbsp;1849 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.pba-lille.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pierre-Auguste Renoir,&nbsp;Le Cabaret de la m&egrave;re Antony &agrave; Bourron-Marlotte, 1866</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet,&nbsp;Le Bateau de p&ecirc;che, 1865 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.metmuseum.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet,&nbsp;Basse-Mar&eacute;e &agrave; Trouville, c.1865 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.liverpoolmuseums.org.uk/picture-of-month/displaypicture.aspx?id=150\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet, Walk,&nbsp;Promenade, route de la ferme Saint-Sim&eacute;on, 1864 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e ici</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;Marine, Le Havre, c.1866 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://ordrupgaard.dk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;Marine, Effet de nuit, 1864 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.nationalgalleries.org/art-and-artists/5658/seascape-shipping-moonlight\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;Caricature d&rsquo;Auguste Vacquerie,&nbsp;c.1854 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.artic.edu/artworks/15826/caricature-of-auguste-vacquerie\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;Caricature of a man with a large nose, 1855/1856 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.artic.edu/artworks/113092/caricature-of-a-man-with-a-large-nose\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;Caricature of L&eacute;on Manchon, c.1858 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.artic.edu/artworks/15800/caricature-of-leon-manchon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;Caricature of a man with a big cigar, 1855/1856 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.artic.edu/artworks/15809/caricature-of-a-man-with-a-big-cigar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener