__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet,&nbsp;D&eacute;jeuner, 1868 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/en/collections/works-in-focus/painting/commentaire_id/the-lunch-18753.html?cHash=c807532237\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul C&eacute;zanne,&nbsp;Une moderne Olympia,&nbsp;1873-1874 ;&nbsp;lien vers le mus&eacute;e&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.musee-orsay.fr/en/collections/works-in-focus/search/commentaire/commentaire_id/une-moderne-olympia-20438.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ici</a></span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Couverture du catalogue de la Deuxi&egrave;me Exposition des Impressionnistes, avril 1876</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Premi&egrave;re de couverture de l&rsquo;Impressioniste: Journal d&rsquo;art,&nbsp;21 avril 1877</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Cham, &ldquo;Exposition des peintures impressionistes&rdquo;, dans&nbsp;Le Charivari,&nbsp;16 avril 1877</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Affiche de la Q