dow Allart, 1824-1825</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Nagasaki Naval Training Center, XIX&egrave;me si&egrave;cle</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;Au caf&eacute; : Agostina Segatori au Tambourin, 1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;P&egrave;re Tanguy,&nbsp;1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;Tracing of &laquo; The Plum Tree Teahouse at Kameido &raquo; of &nbsp;Hiroshige,&nbsp;1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Hiroshige,&nbsp;The Residence with Plum Trees at Kameido (Maison de th&eacute; aux pruniers &agrave; Kameido), 1857</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Verger avec des pruniers en fleurs, 1887</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Hiroshige,&nbsp;Ohashi Atake no Yudachi (Sudden shower over Shin-Ōhashi bridge and Atake, trad. Le pont Ōhashi et Atake sous une averse soudaine),&nbsp;1857</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;Pont avec pluie,&nbsp;1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;Tracing of the Cover of Paris Illustr&eacute;. Le Japon,&nbsp;1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,Courtisane, 1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Keisai Eisen, Courtesan (Courtisane), c.1840, estampe coloris&eacute;e sur papier japonais, 70x24,7cm, dans Paris Illustr&eacute;. Le Japon, n&ordm;45-46, 4 mai 1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent Van Gogh,&nbsp;Autoportrait d&eacute;di&eacute; &agrave; Paul Gauguin, 1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Mutō Shui,&nbsp;The monk Musō Soseki,&nbsp;1349</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;Branche d&acute;amandier en fleurs, 1890</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Grand plat de Koutami d&eacute;cor&eacute; par Morikagh&eacute; (Fin du XVIIe si&egrave;cle). Brule-parfums de Hizen primitif (XVI`si&egrave;cle) ; petite bo&iacute;te de Koutani ; bo&icirc;te et bol, par Kenzan ; bo&icirc;te en forme de personnage, par Ninsei ; bol de Tokio &nbsp;(Pi&egrave;ces c&eacute;ramiques de la collection de M. Louis Gonse) dans Louis Gonse,&nbsp;L&rsquo;Art japonais,&nbsp;tome I, Ed. A. Quantin, Paris, 1883</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anciennes fabriques de Hizen Ice (Banko) Kioto et Satsouma. Plateau, bo&icirc;tes &agrave; parfums, th&eacute;i&egrave;re, statuette, coupes, pitong (Pi&egrave;ces de la collection de M.S. Bing) dans Louis Gonse, L&rsquo;Art japonais,&nbsp;tome II, Ed. A. Quantin, Paris, 1883</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anciennes fabriques de Kioto, Takatori, Koutani et Ice (Banko). Dharma en terre laqu&eacute;e, pr&eacute;sentoir, bouteilles &agrave; saki, pitong, bo&icirc;te &agrave; parfums, coupe en forme de coquille (Pi&egrave;ces de la collection de M.S. Bing) dans Louis Gonse,&nbsp;L&rsquo;Art japonais, tome II, Ed. A. Quantin, Paris, 1883</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Kung Hsien,&nbsp;Tree besides a river (Arbres derri&egrave;re la rivi&egrave;re), 1684</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;Winter Garden (Jardin d&rsquo;hiver au Pays Bas),&nbsp;1884</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;Park with Shrub (Parc),&nbsp;1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;Orchards in Blossom, View of Arles (Vue d&acute;Arles avec vergers en fleur),&nbsp;1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Park with Fence (Parc &agrave; Arles),&nbsp;1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Katsushika Hokusai,&nbsp;Mount Fuji beyond a river bank,&nbsp;1834-1835</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;The Rock of Montmajour with Pine Trees (Le Rocher de Montmajour avec des pins),&nbsp;1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Katsushika Hokusai, Manga (Denshin kaishu), vol. 7, 1817</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Fishing boat at sea, Arles, 1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Katsushika Hokusai,&nbsp;Waves (Vagues), dans Hokusai manga (Denshin kaishu),&nbsp;vol. 7, 1817</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh,&nbsp;De sterrennacht (La Nuit &eacute;toil&eacute;e), 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas,&nbsp;Femme avec chrysanth&egrave;mes, 1865</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Hiroshige, Sanno Festival Procession at Kojimachi I-Chome, (Le Cort&egrave;ge du festival Sannō &agrave; Kōjimachi itchōme), 1856, n&ordm;51, gravure sur bois, 36,4x23,7cm, de la s&eacute;rie&nbsp;Meisho Yedo Hiakkei (Cent vues d&rsquo;Edo)</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Katsushika Hokusai,&nbsp;Brumes de Sandari,&nbsp;1798</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas,&nbsp;Diego Martelli,&nbsp;1879</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Kunisada,&nbsp;Shokunin (Artisans. A group of women in a workshop producing woodblock prints, trad. La fabrication de gravures sur bois), 1857</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;<