ext\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse-Lautrec,&nbsp;Jane Avril, 1899</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">William Nicholson,&nbsp;Sarah Bernhardt,&nbsp;1899</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse Lautrec,&nbsp;Moulin Rouge : La Goulue, 1891</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse Lautrec,&nbsp;Divan Japonais, 1892-1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse Lautrec,&nbsp;Jane Avril. Le caf&eacute; concert,&nbsp;1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gibon Sangai,&nbsp;Takuma Daishi. Faux-cils,&nbsp;1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse Lautrec,&nbsp;La Goulue : valse pour piano, 1894</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse Lautrec, Yvette Guilbert,&nbsp;1894</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Hiroshige,&nbsp;Asakusa tanbu Torinomachi mode (Revelers Returned from the Tori no Machi Festival at Asakusa),&nbsp;1857</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henri de Toulouse Lautrec,&nbsp;May Milton, 1895</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pablo Picasso,&nbsp;La Chambre bleue, 1901</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `videosonline` (`id`, `title_fr`, `subtitle_fr`, `text_fr`, `texto_secondary_fr`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `image`, `color`, `home_image`, `title`, `subtitle`, `text`, `texto_secondary`, `bio`, `ilustraciones`, `order`) VALUES
(10, 'Paul Gauguin sème la zizanie', 'Moderniste génial Colon, pédophile et misogyne Artiste post-genré', '<p>Les premiers historiens associent Paul Gauguin au g&eacute;nie moderne, quand ses paires l\'accusaient de plagiat... Les historiens postmodernes et f&eacute;ministes le d&eacute;peignent en misogyne colonialiste et opportuniste. Plus r&eacute;cemment, des &eacute;tudes l\'associent &agrave; un proto-postcolonialiste remettant en cause la sexualit&eacute; h&eacute;t&eacute;rosexuelle europ&eacute;enne.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&Agrave; m&eacute;thodologies distinctes, interpr&eacute;tations divergentes qui magnifient la richesse de la production de Paul Gauguin. &nbsp;</p>', 'En fonction de leurs allégeances idéologiques, les interprétations de l\'œuvre de Paul Gauguin aboutissent à des conclusions contradictoires.', '2024-10-11 23:13:00', '2024-11-09 02:05:16', 'videosonline/October2024/AEiiZD58sM927wejDpYS.jpg', '#05c8a1', 'videosonline/October2024/2dmI7B841DpywuR0QaqZ.jpg', 'Paul Gauguin sows discord', 'Brilliant modernist Colon, pedophile and misogynist Post-gender artist', '<p>Early historians associated Paul Gauguin with modern genius, while his peers accused him of plagiarism... Postmodern and feminist historians portrayed him as a colonialist and opportunist misogynist. More recently, studies associate him with a proto-postcolonialist questioning European heterosexual sexuality.</p>\r\n<p>Different methodologies, divergent interpretations that magnify the richness of Paul Gauguin\'s production.</p>', 'Depending on their ideological allegiances, interpretations of Paul Gauguin\'s work lead to contradictory conclusions.', '<p>Griselda Pollock, <em>Avant-garde Gambits,</em> 1888-1893: Gender and the Color of Art History, Thames and Hudson, 1993</p>\r\n<p>Frantz Fanon, <em>Peau noire, masques blancs</em>, Seuil, 1952</p>\r\n<p>Stephen F. Eisenman, <em>Gauguin\'s Skirt</em>, Thames &amp; Hudson, 1999&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Bronwen Nicholson, Roger Neich, <em>Gauguin and Maori Art</em>, Univ of Washington pr, 1995</p>', '<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Alfred Barr, Cubism and Abstract Art, 1936</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Hermaphrodite endormi ou hermaphrodite Borgh&egrave;se, copie romane du IIe si&egrave;cle</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Pavillon Javanais, 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, sc&egrave;ne du The Tathagat Meets an Ajiwaka Monk on the Benares Road, Frise du Temple de Borobudur, Java, c. 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, sc&egrave;ne du L\'Assault of Mara, Frise du Temple de Borobudur, Java, c. 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Tahitiennes en robe mission, 1860/1879</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Artemisia Gentileschi, Susanne et les vieillards, 1610</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Bobby Holcomb, O Ta&rsquo;aroa, 1986</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Camille Pissarro, Brouillard &agrave; l&rsquo;Hermitage, Pontoise, 1879</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Camille Pissarro, La Fermi&egrave;re, 1880</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Camille Pissarro, Les Toits rouges, coin de village, effet d\'hiver, 1877</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Charles Georges Spitz, Femme tahitienne (identification suppos&eacute;e &agrave; Teha\'amana), c.1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas, Femme avec chrysanth&egrave;mes, 1865</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas, Le Foyer de la danse &agrave; l&rsquo;op&eacute;ra de la rue Le Peletier, c. 1872</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas, Le Tub, 1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Manet, Olympia ,1863-65</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, Le Pardon de Pont Aven, 1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, Les Chiffonniers ou Pont de fer &agrave; Asni&egrave;res, 1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Francisco de Goya, La Maja nue, 1975-1800</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat, Un dimanche apr&egrave;s midi &agrave; l&rsquo;&icirc;le de la Grande Jatte, 1884-1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gibon Sengai, Amida Butsu Tokyo, XVIII/XIXe</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jacques-Antoine M&oelig;renhout, Voyages aux &icirc;les du Grand Oc&eacute;an, 1837</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Katsushika Hokusai, Cats and puppies, 1912</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Katsushika Hokusai, Man with a pipe crouching, 1912</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Katsushika Hokusai, Sleeping women</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Tintoret, Suzanne et les vieillards, 1555-56</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pablo Picasso, Deux femmes courant sur la plage, 1922</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pablo Picasso, Les Demoiselles d&acute;Avignon, 1907</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pascal Dagnan-Bouveret, Le Pardon en Bretagne, 1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Pascal Dagnan-Bouveret, Les Bretonnes au Pardon, 1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul C&eacute;zanne, Compotier, verre et pommes (Nature morte avec compotier), 1879-82</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul C&eacute;zanne, La Maison du pendu, Auvers-sur-Oise, 1873</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul C&eacute;zanne, Pont de Maincy, 1879</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul-&Eacute;mile Miot, Deux hommes tahitiens, c.1870</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Arearea II (&Eacute;ventail), c.1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Arl&eacute;siennes (Mistral), 1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Bois de la Maison du Jouir, 1902</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Bouddha, c.1895</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Bretonnes causant ou La danse des quatre Bretonnes, 1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Christ au Jardin des Oliviers, 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Couverture du manuscrit L&rsquo;ancien culte mahorie, 1892/ 1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Deux tahitiennes sur la plage, 1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Environs de Rouen avec vache broutant, 1884</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, &Eacute;tude de nu ou Suzanne cousant, 1880</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, &Eacute;ventail au paysage de Martinique, c. 1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Famille tahitienne (Les Baigneurs), 1902</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Hina Tefatou, 1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Ia Orana Maria, 1891</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Idole &agrave; la coquille, 1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Idole &agrave; la perle, 1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Int&eacute;rieur du peintre, rue Carcel, 1881</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La belle Ang&egrave;le, 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La Berg&egrave;re bretonne (Paysage Breton), 1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La Neige &agrave; Vaugirard II ou Jardin sous la neige I, 1879</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La sieste, 1892/1894</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La Vision apr&egrave;s le sermon, 1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Le Christ jaune, 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Les Baigneuses ou La Plage &agrave; Dieppe, 1885</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Le Sorcier d&rsquo;Hiva Oa, 1902</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, L\'Hiver &agrave; Pont-Aven, petit Breton et ramasseuse ou Petit Berger breton (paysage breton), 1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Mahana no atua (Le Jour de Dieu), 1894</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Manao Tupapau (L&rsquo;Esprit des morts veille), 1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Meyer de Haan (sous la lampe), 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Nature morte &agrave; l&rsquo;estampe japonaise ou Nature morte avec ukiyo-e, 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Nature morte &agrave; l\'&eacute;ventail, 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Nature morte au profil de Laval, 1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Nature morte avec t&ecirc;te de cheval, 1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Nature morte avec trois petits chiens, 1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Olympia, copie d\'apr&egrave;s &Eacute;douard Manet, 1891</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Otahi, 1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Pape Moe (Eaux myst&eacute;rieuses), 1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Pot en forme de t&ecirc;te, Autoportrait, 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Rue de Village &agrave; Osny, 1883</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Ta Matete, 1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Te aa no te areois (La graine d&acute;Areois), 1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Te rerioa (Le R&ecirc;ve), 1897</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Te tamari ino atua (Le Fils de Dieu), 1896</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Te nave nave fenua (Pays merveilleux), 1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Les Messagers d\'Oro, illustration dans L&acute;ancien Culte mahorie, 1892/ 1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Vairaumati tei oa (Son nom est Vairauma), 1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">R&eacute;mi Jouan, Reconstitution de la Maison du Jouir de Gauguin &agrave; Atuona, 2009</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Sandro Botticelli, La Naissance de V&eacute;nus, 1484/1485</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Stanhope Forbes, Une Rue en Bretagne, 1881</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Statuette culture moche</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Tatouage marquisien</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Tombe de Nebamun, Th&egrave;bes, c.1350 a. C.</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Kuniyoshi, Mother playing with her children, 1844/1847</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Kunisada, Sumo Triptych, c.1840</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Hiroshige, Vue de Massaki depuis la for&ecirc;t du sanctuaire Suijin, la petite anse d\'Uchigawa et le village de Sekiya, 1857</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vassily Kandinsky, Sans titre (&Eacute;tude pour Composition VII, Premi&egrave;re abstraction), 1910/1913</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincente Minelli, Lust for life (La Vie passionn&eacute;e de Vincent van Gogh), 1956</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `videosonline` (`id`, `title_fr`, `subtitle_fr`, `text_fr`, `texto_secondary_fr`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `image`, `color`, `home_image`, `title`, `subtitle`, `text`, `texto_secondary`, `bio`, `ilustraciones`, `order`) VALUES
(11, 'Le Réalisme sacré de van Gogh', 'Un peintre protestant', '<p>Vincent van Gogh, fils et petit fils de pasteur et pr&eacute;dicateur lui-m&ecirc;me entretint un rapport au monde sensible fa&ccedil;onn&eacute; par sa connaissance de la doctrine protestante.</p>\r\n<p>La mise en &eacute;vidence de cette empreinte religieuse dans son traitement des figures, dans ses obsessions pour le cadrage ou dans son amour du travail appliqu&eacute; invite &agrave; une nouvelle lecture des &oelig;uvres du ma&icirc;tre hollandais.</p>\r\n<p>Une approche hors mythologies convenues.</p>', 'La peinture de Vincent van Gogh comme la projection de sa foi protestante.', '2024-10-11 23:18:00', '2024-11-09 02:00:34', 'videosonline/October2024/hDNJD5Z8nE3Ner2HlcAC.jpg', '#e34927', 'videosonline/October2024/L3BU7eLyUGTrWRSYbtfa.jpg', 'Van Gogh\'s Sacred Realism', 'A Protestant painter', '<p>Vincent van Gogh, son and grandson of a pastor and preacher himself, maintained a relationship with the sensitive world shaped by his knowledge of Protestant doctrine.</p>\r\n<p>The highlighting of this religious imprint in his treatment of figures, in his obsessions with framing or in his love of applied work invites a new reading of the works of the Dutch master.</p>\r\n<p>An approach outside conventional mythologies.</p>', 'Vincent van Gogh\'s painting as a projection of his Protestant faith.', '<p>Debora Silverman, <em>Van Gogh and Gauguin: The Search for Sacred Art</em>, Farrar, Straus and Giroux, 2000 https://vangoghletters.org/vg/</p>', '<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Vestibule de l&rsquo;asile, 1889,&nbsp; craie, brosse et peinture &agrave; l&rsquo;huile sur papier, 61,6x47,1cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Samuel von Hoogstraten, Vue d\'int&eacute;rieur ou Les Pantoufles, 1654-1662, huile sur toile, 103x70cm, Mus&eacute;e du Louvre, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Samuel von Hoogstraten, Vue d\'un corridor, 1662, huile sur toile, 260x140cm, Dyrham Park, Gloucestershire, Royaume-Uni</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Couloir de l&rsquo;asile, 1889, huile et essence en couleur sur craie noir sur papier verg&eacute; rose, 65,1x49,1cm, Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pieter Jansz, Vue du d&eacute;ambulatoire de l&rsquo;&eacute;glise de Grote ou &Eacute;glise St. Bavon. Haarlem, 1635, huile sur panneau de ch&ecirc;ne, 48,4x36.9cm, Staatliche Museen zu Berlin, Berlin, Allemagne</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Armand Cassagne, Dans les ruines, aquarelle, 87x64cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Armand Cassagne, &laquo; Le plein cintre &raquo;, Trait&eacute; pratique de perspective : appliqu&eacute;e au dessin artistique et industriel, Ed. A. Fouraut, Paris, 1889, 1ere1866, pp. 192-193</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Armand Cassagne, Trait&eacute; pratique de perspective : appliqu&eacute;e au dessin artistique et industriel, premi&egrave;re de couverture, Ed. A. Fouraut, Paris, 1889, 1ere1866</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Armand Cassagne, Trait&eacute; d&rsquo;aquarelle, premi&egrave;re de couverture, Ed. A. Fouraut, Paris, 1875, pp. 84-85</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Armand Cassagne, Le Dessin pour tous, perspective exercice, distance, 1862</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, &laquo; Two perspective frames and a paint box &raquo;, 1885, crayon sur papier, 12,4x7,5cm, dans Nuenen Sketchbook 1884-1885, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Armand Cassagne, &laquo; Grande porte de ferme &raquo;, dessin, Guide de l\'alphabet du dessin, ou L\'Art d\'apprendre et d\'enseigner les principes rationnels du dessin d\'apr&egrave;s nature, Ed. Fouraut, Par&iacute;s, 1895, p.4</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Int&eacute;rieur d&rsquo;atelier de tisserand, 1884, crayon, plume et encre, aquarelle sur papier, 31,5x39,9cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Utagawa Kunisada, Un Acteur en Katanaya Hanshichi, 1855, d&eacute;tail droit de diptyque, 36x25cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Boucher vu &agrave; travers une fen&ecirc;tre, 1888, huile sur toile sur carton, 39,7x33,1cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, &Eacute;tude&nbsp; de fen&ecirc;tre &agrave; l&rsquo;asile de Saint-R&eacute;my asylum,, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Fen&ecirc;tre de l&rsquo;atelier de van Gogh &agrave; l\'asile de Saint-R&eacute;my, 1889, craie, broche, peinture &agrave; l&rsquo;huile, aquarelle sur papier, 62x47,6cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Champ de bl&eacute; cl&ocirc;tur&eacute; sous le soleil et les nuages, 1889, craie noire, calame, encre, aquarelle opaque blanche sur papier verg&eacute;, Kr&ouml;ller-M&uuml;ller Museum, Otterlo, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Champ de bl&eacute; sous le soleil levant, Saint R&eacute;m), 1889, huile sur toile, 71x90,5cm, collection particuli&egrave;re</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Toits, vue de l&acute;Atelier de van Gogh, La Haye, 1882, aquarelle, 39x55cm, collection particuli&egrave;re</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Albrecht D&uuml;rer, Homme dessinant une femme couch&eacute;e, 1583, gravure, 7.7x21,4cm, Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Vue de Paris de l&rsquo;appartement de Th&eacute;o,rue Lepic, 1887, huile sur toile, 45,8x38,1cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vue de Paris de l\'appartement de Theo, rue Lepic, r&eacute;flectographie infrarouge de montrant les lignes d\'un outil de dessin pour cr&eacute;er une perspective, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Claes Jansz. Visscher, Dessin de Sint Anthoniepoort, c.1615, Statens Museum for Kunst, National Gallery of Denmark, Danemark&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Drawbridge Heusden, photographie ND</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pont de Langlois, 1902, photographie &nbsp; ND</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pont sur le Canal d&rsquo;Arles &agrave; Bouc, photographie, ND</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pont-levis de l\'&eacute;cluse de Port de Bouc,ND</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Pont de Langlois, 1888, huile sur toile, 49,5x64,5cm, Wallraf-Richartz Museum, K&ouml;ln, Allemagne</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Champ de fleurs, c.1883, huile sur toile sur bois, 48,9x66cm, National Gallery of Art, Washington, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Jardin du fleuriste sur le Schenkweg, 1882, plume et pinceau sur papier, 24x33,4cm, Rijksstudio, Amsterdam, Pays-Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Paysage avec ferme et deux arbres, 1888, plume rouge et encre marron sur mine de plomb sur papier v&eacute;lin, 25,2x34,1cm, National Gallery of Art, Washington, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Bateaux de p&ecirc;che aux Saintes-Maries, 1888, huile sur toile, 65x81,5cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Lettre du 23 Mai 1889 &agrave; Saint R&eacute;my, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Lettre du 5 Ao&ucirc;t 1882 &agrave; La Haye, d&eacute;tail du croquis, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, carnet d&rsquo; Auvers-sur-Oise, page avec cadre de perspective, 1890, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Bo&icirc;te chinoise laqu&eacute;e avec seize pelotes de laine ayant appartenu &agrave; Vincent van Gogh, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Champ de bl&eacute; avec cypr&egrave;s, 1889, huile sur toile, 73,2x93,4cm, Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Les Mangeurs de pomme de terre, 1885, huile sur toile, 82x114cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, M&eacute;tier avec tisserand, 1884, huile sur toile sur bois, 47,5x61cm, Museum Boijmans Van Beuningen, Rotterdam, Pays-Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Tisserand vu de face, 1884, huile sur toile, Kr&ouml;ller-M&uuml;ller Museum, Otterlo, Pays-Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Tisserand, 1884, crayon, plume, encre et aquarelle sur papier, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Souvenir du jardin &agrave; Etten, 1889, huile sur toile, 73x92cm, Hermitage Museum, Saint-P&eacute;tersbourg, Russie</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Fleurs sauvages et chardon dans un vase, 1890, 67x47cm, collection particuli&egrave;re</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Vase avec roses et mauves, 1890, huile sur toile, 42,2x29cm,&nbsp; Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Nature morte verre de fleurs sauvages, 1890, huile sur toile, 41x34cm, collection particuli&egrave;re</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Oliviers &agrave; Saint R&eacute;my, 1889, huile sur toile, 45,5x59,1cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), Les quatre Heures de la journ&eacute;e grav&eacute; : Le soir, 1867, pastel et crayon cont&eacute; noir, 43,8x54cm, Museum of Fine Arts, Boston, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Veill&eacute;e, 1889, d\'apr&egrave;s Millet, huile sur toile, 74,2x93cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Paysage avec carriole et train, 1890, huile sur toile, 72x90cm, The National Pushkin Museum, Moscou, Russie</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Champs avec coquelicots, 1889, huile sur toile, 72x91cm, Kunsthalle Bremen, Br&ecirc;me, Allemagne</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">L&eacute;on Lhermitte, Le Labourage, 1887, gravure, dans Andr&eacute; Theuriet, La Vie rustique, Ed. C. Taillandier, Paris, 1889, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">L&eacute;on Lhermitte, Les B&ucirc;cherons, 1887, gravure, dans Andr&eacute; Theuriet, La Vie rustique, Ed. C. Taillandier, Paris, 1889, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">L&eacute;on Lhermitte, Le Jardinage, 1887, gravure, dans Andr&eacute; Theuriet, La Vie rustique, Ed. C. Taillandier, Paris, 1889, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet, L&rsquo;Ang&eacute;lus, 1857-1859, huile sur toile, 55,5x66cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, L&rsquo;Ang&eacute;lus du soir, 1880, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Millet, craie noire et rouge, crayon, sanguine, lavis,&nbsp; rehauss&eacute;e au blanc, sur papier verg&eacute; gris bleu&acirc;tre, Kr&ouml;ller-M&uuml;ller Museum, Otterlo, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet, Deux paysans b&ecirc;chant, 1855-1856, gravure sur papier verg&eacute; cr&egrave;me, 23,5x33,5cm, Museum of fine Arts, Boston, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Les B&ecirc;cheurs d\'apr&egrave;s Millet, 1880,, crayon, craie noire sur papier, Kr&ouml;ller-M&uuml;ller Museum, Otterlo, Pays Bas &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), Le Moissonneur &agrave; la faucille dans Les Travaux des champs,, 1853, gravure, 13,5x7,5cm, Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Moissonneur &agrave; la faucille, 1881, d\'apr&egrave;s Millet, Uehara Museum of Modern Art, Shimoda, Japon</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet, Le Semeur,1851, lithographie sur papier asiatique cr&egrave;me obscur, 19,5x16,2cm, Museum of Fine Arts, Boston, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Semeur d\'apr&egrave;s Millet, 1881, crayon, plume et pinceau et encre, aquarelle sur papier, 48,1x36,7cm,&nbsp; Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Vieil homme aupr&egrave;s d&rsquo;un feu, 1881, craie noire et orange-rouge&acirc;tre, lavis gris et brun-rouge&acirc;tre, aquarelle opaque sur papier verg&eacute;, Kr&ouml;ller-M&uuml;ller Museum, Otterlo, Pays Bas &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Terrassier, 1882, lithographie, 58,1x45,3cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Femme &agrave; la brouette, 1883, craie noire naturelle, crayon lithographique, lavis, plume et pinceau sur encre, aquarelle opaque blanche et gris, sur papier verg&eacute;, Kr&ouml;ller-M&uuml;ller Museum, Otterlo, Pays Bas &nbsp;<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet, Les Glaneuses, 1857, huile sur toile, 83,5x110cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Paysanne arrachant de l\'herbe, 1885, craie noire, 51,4x41,5cm, Museum Folkwang, Essen, Allemagne</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), Les Travaux des champs, gravure sur bois, dans L&rsquo;Illustration, 7 f&eacute;vrier 1853</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Semeur, 1889, huile sur toile, 80x64cm, collection particuli&egrave;re</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Sieste ou M&eacute;ridienne, 1889-1890, huile sur toile, 73x90cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), La Sieste, 1853, dans L&rsquo;Illustration, 7 f&eacute;vrier 1853</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), La Broyeuse de lin, 1853, de la s&eacute;rie Les Travaux des champs, 1853, dix gravures sur bois sur papier, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Broyeuse de lin d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Millet, 1889, huile sur toile, 40x26cm,&nbsp; Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Botteleur, 1889, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Millet, huile sur toile, 44,5x33,1cm,&nbsp; Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), Le Botteleur, de la s&eacute;rie Les Travaux des champs, 1853, dix gravures sur bois sur papier, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Faucheur d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Millet, 1889, huile sur toile, 43,5x25cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), Le Faucheur, de la s&eacute;rie Les Travaux des champs, 1853, dix gravures sur bois sur papier, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Fileuse d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Millet, 1889, huile sur toile, 40x25cm, collection particuli&egrave;re</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), La fileuse, de la s&eacute;rie Les Travaux des champs, 1853, dix gravures sur bois sur papier, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Batteur de bl&eacute; d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Millet, 1889, huile sur toile, 42x28cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet (dessin), Adrien Lavieille (graveur), Le Batteur de bl&eacute;, 1853, gravure sur papier chinois noir et gris fix&eacute; sur papier v&eacute;lin blanc opaque, 13,5x7,5cm, The Art Institute of Chicago, Chicago, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet, Les Planteurs de pommes de terre, crayon noir et en couleurs, pastel sur papier, 33,3x42,5cm, ND</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Les Planteurs de pommes de terre d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Millet, 1885, huile sur toile, 33x45cm, Kunsthaus Z&uuml;rich, Z&uuml;rich, Suisse</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Autoportrait au chevalet, 1886, huile sur toile, 46,5x38,5cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Autoportrait &agrave; la pipe et &agrave; la paille, 1887, huile sur toile, 41,9x30,1cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Peintre allant au travail, 1888, d&eacute;truit</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Lettre &agrave; &Eacute;mile Bernard du 19 juin 1888, &agrave; Arles, d&eacute;tail du croquis, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Semeur au soleil couchant, 1888, Kroller-M&uuml;ller, Otterlo, Pays-Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Le Christ endormi pendant la temp&ecirc;te, c.1853, huile sur toile, 50,8x61cm, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Semeur, 1888, huile sur toile, 32,5x40,3cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas, ND</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Carbonel, &laquo; Vannier&raquo;, santon proven&ccedil;al, non document&eacute;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Cr&egrave;che de No&euml;l aux Saintes-Maries-de-la-Mer, photographie</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Acteurs de la pastorale Maurel &agrave; Ch&acirc;teau-Gombert, c.1926, photographie&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Yvan Audouard, La Pastorale des santons de Provence, 2004, couverture du disque</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet, Tondeuse de moutons, 1853, gravure, 13,6x7,4cm, de la s&eacute;rie Les Travaux des Champs, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Tondeuse de moutons, 1889, huile sur toile, 43,6x29,5cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Berceuse (Augustine Roulin), 1889, huile sur toile, 92,7x73,7cm, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Madame Roulin rocking the cradle (La Berceuse), 1889, huile sur toile, 92,7x73,8cm, The Art Institute of Chicago, Chicago, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Augustine Roulin (La Berceuse), 1889, huile sur toile, Stedelijk Museum Amsterdam, Amsterdam, Pays-Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Berceuse (Portrait de Madame Roulin), huile sur toile, Kroller-M&uuml;ller, Otterlo, Pays-Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Lullaby : Madame Augustine Roulin Rocking a Cradle (La Berceuse), 1889, 92,7x73,7cm, Museum of Fine Arts, Boston, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">G&eacute;rard David, La Vierge &agrave; la soupe au lait, c.1515, ch&ecirc;ne, 35x29cm, Mus&eacute;es royaux des Beaux-Arts de Belgique, Bruxelles, Belgique</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pieter Aertsen, L\'&Eacute;tal du boucher avec la fuite en Egypte, 1551, huile sur panneau, 115,6x168,9cm, Collections d\'art de l\'universit&eacute;, l\'Universit&eacute; d\'Uppsala, Su&egrave;de.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Les Saintes-Maries-de-la-Mer, La procession de mai et d&rsquo;octobre, carte postale, Arles&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Ex-Voto marin, Chapelle Notre-Dame des Anges, Pignans</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Ex-Voto marin, Bouc-Bel-Air&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Naufrage, Ex-V. F. G. A Carlo Vian, 12 avril 1832, Sanctuaire de Notre-Dame de Laghet, La Trinit&eacute;&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pierre Loti, P&ecirc;cheur d&rsquo;Islande, couverture, Ed. Calmann-L&eacute;vy, Paris 1893</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Fromentin, Les Ma&icirc;tres d&rsquo;autrefois, premi&egrave;re de couverture, Ed. E. Plon et Cie, Paris, 1876</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jan van Eyck, La Vierge &agrave; la fontaine, 1439, huile sur bois, Mus&eacute;e Royal des Beaux-Arts d\'Anvers, Anvers, Belgique</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jan van Eyck, Vierge et enfant au chanoine van der Paele, 1436, 160x124,5cm, Groeninge Museum Bruges, Bruges, Belgique</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Hans Memling, Vierge &agrave; l&acute;enfant, 1480, huile sur ch&ecirc;ne, 54,2x37,4cm,&nbsp; The National Gallery, Londres, Royaume-Uni&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, Le Pardon de Pont-Aven, 1888, huile sur toile, 93x74cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris, France&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Pardon d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Bernard, 1888, aquarelle, 60x73,3cm, Civica Galleria d&rsquo;Arte Moderna, Milan, Italie</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;glise Saint-Andr&eacute;, &agrave; Anvers, vitrail, visit&eacute;e le 2 janvier 1886</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Autoportrait d&eacute;di&eacute; &agrave; Paul Gauguin, 1888, huile sur toile, 61,5x50,3cm, Fogg Art Museum, Harvard University, Cambridge, &Eacute;tats-Unis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Autoportrait avec portrait de Bernard, \'Les Mis&eacute;rables\', 1888, huile sur toile, 44,5x50,3cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Deborah Silverman, Van Gogh and Gauguin, couverture, Ed. Farrar, Straus and Giroux, 2000</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Lettre &agrave; Th&eacute;o du 23 mai 1889, Saint-R&eacute;my, d&eacute;tail du croquis, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `videosonline` (`id`, `title_fr`, `subtitle_fr`, `text_fr`, `texto_secondary_fr`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `image`, `color`, `home_image`, `title`, `subtitle`, `text`, `texto_secondary`, `bio`, `ilustraciones`, `order`) VALUES
(12, 'Gauguin versus van Gogh', 'Quand les différends spirituels compromettent la communion artistique', '<p>On se r&eacute;f&egrave;re volontiers &agrave; une suppos&eacute;e incompatibilit&eacute; de temp&eacute;rament pour expliquer la querelle qui opposa Paul Gauguin &agrave; Vincent van Gogh.</p>\r\n<p>Une approche spirituelle est &eacute;galement productive : chacun avait re&ccedil;u une solide &eacute;ducation religieuse, protestante pour l\'un, catholique pour l\'autre ; ils en conserv&egrave;rent deux conceptions du monde r&eacute;ciproquement intol&eacute;rables, rendant toute communion artistique conflictuelle.</p>', 'La confrontation entre Vincent van Gogh et Paul Gauguin ravive la guerre des images comme au temps de la Réforme et Contre-Réforme.', '2024-10-11 23:24:00', '2024-11-09 01:48:12', 'videosonline/October2024/HbZERNY4XZM3FBEvwARg.jpg', '#807ef2', 'videosonline/October2024/vayHZBI5Ibos6KDLP5xr.jpg', 'Gauguin versus van Gogh', 'When spiritual differences compromise artistic communion', '<p>A supposed incompatibility of temperament is often cited to explain the quarrel between Paul Gauguin and Vincent van Gogh.</p>\r\n<p>A spiritual approach is also productive: each had received a solid religious education, Protestant for one, Catholic for the other; they retained two mutually intolerable conceptions of the world, making any artistic communion conflictual.</p>', 'The confrontation between Vincent van Gogh and Paul Gauguin rekindles the war of images as in the time of the Reformation and Counter-Reformation.', '<p>Debora Silverman, <em>Van Gogh and Gauguin: The Search for Sacred Art</em>, Farrar, Straus and Giroux, 2000</p>\r\n<p>https://vangoghletters.org/vg/&nbsp;<em>La Correspondance de Paul Gauguin</em>, Victor Merlh&egrave;s, Fondation Singer-Polignac, 1984</p>', '<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Autoportrait &laquo; d&eacute;di&eacute; &agrave; mon Ami Paul Gauguin &raquo;, 1888, huile sur toile, 61,5x50,3cm, Fogg Art Museum, Harvard University, Cambrige, &Eacute;tats-Unis 1:32(1), 4:33(1), 9:38(1), 17:56(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Autoportrait avec portrait d\'&Eacute;mile Bernard, 1888, huile sur toile, 44,5x50,3cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays-Bas&nbsp; 1:53(1), 8:36(1), 9:38(1), 2:45(2), 17:40(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Autoportrait &agrave; l\'ami Laval, 1888, huile sur toile, 46x38cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 2:30(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, Autoportrait avec portrait de Paul Gauguin, 1888, huile sur toile, 46x56cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays-Bas&nbsp; 2:03(1), 01:19(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Charles Laval, Autoportrait &agrave; l\'Ami Vincent, 1888, huile sur toile, 50,7x60,4cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays-Bas&nbsp; 2:35(1),&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Louis Gonse, L&rsquo;Art japonais, tome II, Ed. A, Quantin, Paris, 1883, p. 348, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; 3:59(1)&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Semeur, 1888, huile sur toile, 32,5x40,3cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays Bas&nbsp; 6:23(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Pot en forme de t&ecirc;te, autoportrait, 1889, The Danish Museum of Arts and design, Copenhague, Danemark &nbsp; 14:27(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Le Pouldu. Entr&eacute;e de la rivi&egrave;re et grotte St. Julien &raquo;, carte postale&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:03(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Christ au jardin des oliviers, 1889, huile sur toile, 73x92cm, Norton Gallery of Art, West palm Beach, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 15:50(1), 19:20(1), 8:40(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Le Pouldu. L\'H&ocirc;tel des Grands Sables &raquo;, carte postale, ND &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Le Pouldu (Finist&egrave;re). Restaurant de la poste et de la plage &raquo;, carte postale, ND &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 17:05(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Arles. Portique de l&rsquo;&eacute;glise Saint-Trophime &raquo;, carte postale, Ed. Baryelon, ND&nbsp; &nbsp; 19:38(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Epithelioma tubule de nez &raquo;, 1872, impression &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine, Paris, The Burns Archive, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 20:24(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">C. Heish, &laquo; Photographs of a large Rodent Cancer before Operation. &raquo;, figure 1, photographie, 1867 dans Dr. Charles Hewitt Moore, Rodent Cancer, Ed. Longmans, Green, and Co, Londres, 1867, p. 128 &nbsp; 20:24(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">C. Heish, &laquo; Photographs of a large Rodent Cancer before Operation. &raquo;, figure 2, photographie, 1867 dans Dr. Charles Hewitt Moore, Rodent Cancer, Ed. Longmans, Green, and Co, Londres, 1867, p. 128 &nbsp; 20:24(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Salle de l&rsquo;h&ocirc;pital Saint-R&eacute;my, 1889, huile sur toile, 72x91cm, Oskar Reinhart Collection \'Am R&ouml;merholz\', Winterthur, Suisse &nbsp; 21:17(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Maison jaune ou La Rue, 1888, huile sur toile, 72X91,5cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays-Bas &nbsp; 3:26(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">La Maison jaune, photographie, ND&nbsp; 3:48(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Arles. Les Alyscamps. All&eacute;e des Tombeaux &raquo;, carte postale,ND 4:23(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pieter Saenredam, Int&eacute;rieur de l&rsquo;&eacute;glise Saint-Bavon, Haarlem, 1648, huile sur panneau, 174,80x143,60cm, Scottish National Gallery, &Eacute;dimbourg, &Eacute;cosse &nbsp; 6:32(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Les Alyscamps ou L&rsquo;All&eacute;e des Alyscamps, 1888, huile sur toile, 92x73,5cm, collection particuli&egrave;re 4:46(2)? 5:23(2), 8:22(2)&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, L&rsquo;All&eacute;e des Peupliers en Automne, 1884, huile sur toile sur panneau, 65,7x99cm, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays-Bas&nbsp; 5:09(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Armand Cassagne, &laquo; Croquis d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s nature. Application de la r&egrave;gle 86 &raquo;, dessin, dans&nbsp; Armand Cassagne, Trait&eacute; pratique de perspective, Ed. A. Fouraut, Paris, 1889, p. 68 5:13(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Avenue des Peupliers, 1884, crayon, plume et encre sur papie