ier, Ratapoil, c.1851, sculpture, bronze patin&eacute;, 43,5cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; 23:12(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Les Buveurs, 1890, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Honor&eacute; Daumier, huile sur toile, 59,4x73,4cm, The Art Institute of Chicago, Chicago, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; 24:02(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Vigne rouge (&agrave; Montmajour, Arles v), 1888, huile sur toile, 73x91cm, Mus&eacute;e des Beaux-Arts de Pushkin, Saint P&eacute;tersbourg, Russie&nbsp; 24:53(2), 26:13(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Les Vendanges &agrave; Arles ou Mis&egrave;res humaines, 1888, huile sur jute, 72,5x92cm, Museum Ordrupgaard, J&aelig;gersborg Dyrehave, Danemark &nbsp; 27:25(2), 15:15(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Nature morte aux fruits et visage &laquo; d&eacute;di&eacute;e &agrave; Laval &raquo;, 1888, huile sur toile, 43x58cm, Mus&eacute;e des Beaux-Arts de Pushkin, Saint P&eacute;tersbourg, Russie 19:32(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, En pleine chaleur ou Les Cochons, 1888, huile sur toile, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 15:57(3), 22:18(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Chronique locale &raquo;, dans Le Forum r&eacute;publicain, 30 d&eacute;cembre 1888, &agrave; Arles&nbsp; 29:43(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, &laquo; La Cour d\'honneur du petit s&eacute;minaire dioc&eacute;sain lors de son ouverture &raquo;, carte postale, ND&nbsp; &nbsp; 1:25(3)?</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Fran&ccedil;ois-Marie Gobinet de Villecholle, Portrait de F&eacute;lix Dupanloup, c.1876, ND 1:41(3)?</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Bertall, &laquo; L&rsquo;&eacute;cole tiraill&eacute;e entre l&rsquo;&Eacute;tat et l&rsquo;&Eacute;glise &raquo;, dans Le Journal pour Rire, 23 f&eacute;vrier 1850 &nbsp; &nbsp; 1:50(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix Dupanloup, De la haute &eacute;ducation intellectuelle, couverture, Ed. C. Douniol, Paris, 1866&nbsp; &nbsp; 2:55(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix Dupanloup, De L&rsquo;&eacute;ducation, couverture, Ed. C. Douniol, Paris, 1862 &nbsp; 2:55(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix Dupanloup, Manuel des cat&eacute;chismes, couverture, Ed. P. Devarenne, Paris, 1851 &nbsp; 4:20(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Peter Paul Rubens, Die Heilige C&auml;cilie (Sainte C&eacute;cile), c.1639-1640, huile sur panneau, 180,6x142,7cm, Staatliche Museen zu Berlin, Berlin, Allemagne &nbsp; 7:40(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Peter Paul Rubens, Les Miracles de Saint Ignace de Loyola, c.1617-1618, toile, 535x395cm, Kunsthistorisches Museum Wien, Vienne, Autriche&nbsp; &nbsp; 12:18(3), 31:30(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Bo&icirc;te sculpt&eacute;e, c.1884-1885, bois de poirier avec jointure m&eacute;tal, cuir et tache rouge, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 14:02(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Julie Laurberg, Paul Gauguin et Mette Sophie Gad, 1885, Royal Danish Library, Copenhagen, Danemark &nbsp; 14:19(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Manzana-Pisarro, Gauguin chez Durand Ruel, 1893 &nbsp; 17:23(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, &Egrave;ve bretonne, 1889, aquarelle et pastel sur papier, 33,7x31,1cm, McNay Art Museum, Texas, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; 21:12(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Momie tr&eacute;pan&eacute;e de Piedra grande del Utcubamba, Chachapoyas, P&eacute;rou &raquo;,&nbsp; Mus&eacute;e de l&rsquo;Homme, Paris&nbsp; 21 :40(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Dans les Vagues ou Ondine (I), 1889, huile sur toile, 92,5x72,4cm, The Cleveland Museum of Art, Cleveland, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; 21:49(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La Vie et la mort ou Femme se baignant, 1889, huile su toile, 92x73cm, The Mahmoud Khalil Museum, Le Caire, &Eacute;gypte &nbsp; 22:32(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Portrait de Clovis Gauguin ou&nbsp; L&rsquo;Enfant endormi, 1884, huile sur toile, 46x55,5cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 24:09(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Manao Tupapau ou L&rsquo;Esprit des morts veille, 1892, huile sur toile, 73x92cm, Albright-Knox Art Gallery, Buffalo, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La Petite r&ecirc;ve : &eacute;tude, 1881, huile sur toile, 60x74cm, Ordrupgaard Museum, Copenhague, Danemark &nbsp; 24:48(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La Vision apr&egrave;s le sermon, 1888, huile sur toile, 73x92cm, National Gallery of Scotland, &Eacute;dimbourg, &Eacute;cosse &nbsp; 25:13(3), 27:20(3), 30:27(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, La Berg&egrave;re bretonne, 1886, huile sur toile, 60x73cm, Laing Art Gallery, Newcastle-upon-Tyne, Royaume-Uni&nbsp; 26:55(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Paysage breton avec porcher, 1888, huile sur toile, 73x93cm, Los Angeles County Museum of Art, Los Angeles, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; 26:55(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Une Classe de gar&ccedil;ons, &eacute;cole d\'Hellemmes, Nord, photographie, vers la fin du XIXe si&egrave;cle, Archives d&eacute;partementales du Nord, Lille&nbsp; 27:13(3) &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Richard Hall, La Classe manuelle. &Eacute;cole de petites filles, 1889, &nbsp;Mus&eacute;e des beaux-Arts de Rennes, Rennes&nbsp; 27:20(3) &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Sahib Svelt, &laquo; Leur examen de conscience. Vingt ans &raquo;, dans La Vie parisienne, 31 mars 1888, p.177,&nbsp; Biblioth&egrave;que de l&rsquo;institut de France, Paris&nbsp; 27:52(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Abram, Pri&egrave;re &agrave; Locronan, 1887 &nbsp; 28:08(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Richard Hall, Le V&oelig;u - Bretagne, 1887</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Alexandre Antigna, Marchand d&rsquo;images, c.1862, huile sur toile, 143x113cm, &nbsp;Mus&eacute;e des Beaux-Arts de Bordeaux, Bordeaux &nbsp; 28:35(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Am&eacute;d&eacute;e Gu&eacute;rard, L&rsquo;Enfant malade, 1870, huile sur toile, 60x92cm, Mus&eacute;e d&eacute;partemental breton Quimper, Quimper, France &nbsp; 29:01(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Nicolas J.L., Notre-Dame-de-Rumengol, 1858, estampe d&rsquo;&Eacute;pinal, bois de fil colori&eacute; au pochoir sur papier et impression typographique du texte, 64x42cm, Ed. Pellerin,&nbsp; Mus&eacute;e d&eacute;partemental breton Quimper, Quimper, France 29:20(3) &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Galerie religieuse. Sacr&eacute; C&oelig;ur de Marie, 1836,&nbsp; estampe d&rsquo;&Eacute;pinal, gravure sur bois en couleur, 60x40cm, Ed. Pellerin, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 30:16(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Fran&ccedil;ois Georgin, Le Miroir du p&ecirc;cheur, 1830, estampe d&rsquo;&Eacute;pinal, gravure sur bois en couleur, Ed. Pellerin, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 30:21(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Berceuse , Augustine Roulin, 1889, huile sur toile, 92,7x73,7cm, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York &nbsp; &nbsp; 31:54(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, &Eacute;mile Bernard et Vincent Van Gogh sur les berges de la Seine &agrave; Asni&egrave;res, c.1886, aristotype, 132&times;160 mm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 1:04(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, Le Pardon de Pont-Aven, 1888, huile sur toile, 93&times;74cm, Josefowitz collection, Lausanne, Suisse &nbsp; 1:42(4)&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Le Pardon de Pont-Aven d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s &Eacute;mile Bernard, 1888, aquarelle, 60x73,3cm, Civica Galleria d&rsquo;Arte Moderna, Milan, Italie &nbsp; 2:09(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, Crucifixion ou Christ, 1894, gravure sur bois sur papier verg&eacute;, 35x14,7cm, Brooklyn Museum, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 3:50(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, L&rsquo;Adoration des bergers ou Nativit&eacute;, 1889, estampe, bois et aquarelle, 60,3x47,1cm, Biblioth&egrave;que de l\'Institut National d\'Histoire de l\'Art, collections Jacques Doucet, Paris &nbsp; 3:40(4), 5:34(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, Christ rencontrant sa m&egrave;re, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; 3:50(4), 5:34(4), 7:09(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard,&nbsp; Christ au Jardin des Oliviers, collection particuli&egrave;re 3:50(4), 5:34(4), 7:18(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;mile Bernard, Christ jaune, 1889, huile sur toile, 68x58,42cm, Indianapolis Museum of Art, Indianapolis, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 8:06(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, Oliviers avec ciel jaune et soleil, 1889, huile sur toile, &nbsp;92,7x73,7cm, The Minneapolis Institute of Arts, Minnesota, Etats-Unis&nbsp; 9:26(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Vincent van Gogh, La Cueillette des olives, 1889, huile sur toile, 73,3x92,2cm, Kr&ouml;ller-M&uuml;ller Museum, Otterlo, Pays-Bas &nbsp; 9:49(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Le Calvaire breton ou Christ vert, 1889, huile sur toile, 92x73,5cm, Mus&eacute;es royaux des Beaux-Arts de Belgique, Bruxelles, Belgique&nbsp; 10:48(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Calvaire de Nizon, statue, Place de l&rsquo;&Eacute;glise, Pont-Aven&nbsp; 11:19(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">La Maison-Mus&eacute;e de Pouldu, photographie de l&rsquo;int&eacute;rieur, Clohars-Carno&euml;t, France&nbsp; 13:18(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Jeanne d\'Arc ou Jeune Bretonne au rouet, 1889, huile sur pl&acirc;tre, Mus&eacute;e Van Gogh, Amsterdam, Pays-Bas &nbsp; 13:37(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">F&eacute;lix Dupanloup, Second pan&eacute;gyrique de Jeanne d\'Arc, couverture, Orl&eacute;ans, 1869, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 14:20(4)&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, D\'o&ugrave; venons-nous ? Que sommes-nous ? O&ugrave; allons-nous ?, c.1897-1898, huile sur toile, 139,1x374,6cm, The Museum of Fine Arts, Boston, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:21(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, Lettre autographe avec dessin original, &agrave; Daniel de Monfreid, Tahiti, f&eacute;vrier 1898, Mus&eacute;e du Louvre, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:55(4)&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Gauguin, L&rsquo;Esprit moderne et le catholicisme, 1902, couverture frontale et couverture arri&egrave;re, monotypes en noir et marron sur papier japonais, 28x19cm, Saint Louis Art Museum, Missouri, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 17:34(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `videosonline` (`id`, `title_fr`, `subtitle_fr`, `text_fr`, `texto_secondary_fr`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `image`, `color`, `home_image`, `title`, `subtitle`, `text`, `texto_secondary`, `bio`, `ilustraciones`, `order`) VALUES
(13, 'Anarchie sexuelle, I', 'Norme puritaine Implosion du système', '<p>La femme s\'&eacute;mancipe, enfourche une bicyclette et enfile le pantalon, dont le port est pourtant interdit par le code civil. &Ocirc; scandale ! Mais qui sont ces nouvelles amazones, ces vampiresses fantasm&eacute;es par les arts quand la r&eacute;alit&eacute; quotidienne de la majorit&eacute; d\'entre elles s\'arr&ecirc;te aux murs de la domesticit&eacute; ?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Histoire d\'une c&eacute;l&egrave;bre duperie, vue &agrave; travers peintures, sculptures et bijoux d&acute;une &eacute;poque qui v&eacute;n&egrave;re autant qu\'elle craint la dite &laquo; Femme Nouvelle &raquo;.</p>', 'Les sciences légitiment la peur ancestrale de l’émancipation féminine tandis que les arts alimentent  le débat, renforçant les préjugés tout en fantasmant la femme libre.', '2024-10-11 23:30:00', '2024-11-09 01:30:49', 'videosonline/November2024/yWHmKMsbO3zGp071lm2C.jpg', '#322688', 'videosonline/October2024/EF5rvaldqT0mCn8jwulc.jpg', 'Sexual Anarchy, I', 'Puritan Standard Implosion of the system', '<p>The woman emancipates herself, mounts a bicycle and puts on pants, the wearing of which is nevertheless forbidden by the civil code. Oh scandal! But who are these new Amazons, these vampires fantasized by the arts when the daily reality of the majority of them stops at the walls of domesticity?&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Story of a famous deception, seen through paintings, sculptures and jewelry of an era that venerates as much as it fears the so-called \"<em>New Woman</em>\".</p>', 'Science legitimizes the ancestral fear of female emancipation while the arts fuel the debate, reinforcing prejudices while fantasizing about the free woman.', '<p>Joseph A. Kestner, <em>Mythology and Misogyny: The Social Discourse of Nineteenth Century British Classical-Subject Painting</em>, The University of Wisconsin Press, 1989</p>\r\n<p>Shearer West , <em>Fin de Si&egrave;cle</em>, Overlook press, 1994</p>\r\n<p>Bram Dijkstra, <em>Idols of Perversity, Fantasies of Feminine Evil in Fin-de-Si&egrave;cle Culture</em>, Oxford University Press, 1986</p>', '<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Elaine Showalter, Sexual Anarchy: Gender and Culture at the Fin de Si&egrave;cle, couverture, Ed. Virago, Londres, 1992</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Baptiste Lesueur, Club patriotique de femmes, 1789-1795</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Lock and Whitfield, Charles Darwin, 1877</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Herbert Spencer, 1849</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Fritz Luckhardt, Carl Vogt, c.1870</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Broca, c.1860</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Nicholas Francis Cooke, Satan in society, premi&egrave;re de couverture, Ed. Vent Company, Chicago, 1890</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Nicholas Francis Cooke, photographie dans Nicholas Francis Cooke, Satan in society, premi&egrave;re de couverture, Ed. Vent Company, Chicago, 1890</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">George Elgar Hicks, Mrs. Hicks, Mary, Rosa and Elgar, ca.1857</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">George Elgar Hicks, Woman&rsquo;s Mission I: Guide of Childhood (La Mission de la femme : guide de l\'enfance), 1863</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">George Elgar Hicks, Woman&rsquo;s Mission II: Companion of Manhood (</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">La Mission de la femme : compagne de l\'homme), 1863</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">George Elgar Hicks, Woman&rsquo;s Mission III: Comfort of Old Age (</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">La Mission de la femme : r&eacute;confort de la vieillesse), 1863</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Abbott Handerson Thayer, A Virgin (Une vierge), 1892-1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">William Bouguereau, La Frileuse, 1879</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">L&eacute;on Bazille Perrault, Putto endormi, 1882</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Elimar Ulrich Bruno Piglhein, Christmas Morning (Le Matin de No&euml;l), c.1890</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Carri&egrave;re, Maternit&eacute;, c.1892</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Giovanni Segantini, The Angel of Life (L\'Ange de la vie), 1894-1895</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Giovanni Segantini, Fruit of love (Le Fruit de l&acute;amour), 1891</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Abbott Handerson Thayer, Angel (Ange), 1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Louis Ridel, Derni&egrave;res Fleurs, 1900, dans Henri Frantz, Le salon de 1900 and the Decennial Exhibition, Ed. Manzi, Joyant, Paris, New York, 1900</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Francis Bernard Dicksee, The Confession (La Confession ou L&rsquo;Aveu), 1896</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Leonhard de Jonghe, Die Genesung (La Convalescente), 1893</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Carl Larsson, The Invalid ou Convalescence,1899</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Francis Bernard Dicksee, The Crisis (La Crise), 1891</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Edvard Munch, The Sick child (La jeune Fille malade), 1885-1886</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Lawrence Alma Tadema, A Silent Greeting (Adieu silencieux), 1889</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">James Whistler, Symphony in white, no. III (Symphonie en blanc, no. III), 1865-1867</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Frederic Leighton, Flaming June (Juin flamboyant), c.1895</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Albert Joseph Moore, Midsummer (Plein &Eacute;t&eacute;), 1887</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Albert Joseph Moore, Apples (Pomme), 1875</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Albert Joseph Moore, Dreamers (R&ecirc;veuses), 1850-1882</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Albert Joseph Moore, A Workbasket, 1879</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Albert Joseph Moore, A Sleeping Girl, c. 1875</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John William Waterhouse, &laquo; I am sick of shadows &raquo; said the Lady of Shalott (Dame de Shalott), 1915</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John William Waterhouse, The Lady of Shalott (La Dame de Shalott), 1888</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, Oph&eacute;lie, 1851-1852</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Arthur Hugues, Ophelia (Oph&eacute;lie), c.1852</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Ernest H&eacute;bert, Oph&eacute;lie, 1890</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">George du Maurier, Trilby, 1894</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">George du Maurier, Amstrong Margaret, Trilby: a Novel, frontispice, Ed. Harper and Bros, New York, 1894</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Maximilian Lenz, A world (R&ecirc;verie), 1899</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Dante Gabriel Rossetti, The Day Dream (R&ecirc;verie), 1880</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Evelyn de Morgan, The Dryad (La Dryade), 1884</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John William Waterhouse, Daphn&eacute; et Apollon, 1908</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John William Waterhouse, Phyllis et D&eacute;mophon, 1897</span><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">William Adolp