xui-rich-text__text\">Gustav Klimt, L&rsquo;Attente, Frise Stoclet, 1905-1909, couleur sur carton, 193,5x115cm, &Ouml;sterreichisches Museum f&uuml;r angewandte Kunst, Vienne, Autriche &nbsp; 17:00(4) &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustav Klimt, Le Baiser, 1907-1908, huile sur toile, 180x180, &Ouml;sterreichische Galerie Belvedere, Vienne, Autriche&nbsp; 17:20(4), 19:25(4) &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">John William Waterhouse, &Eacute;cho et Narcisse, 1903, huile sur toile, 109,2x189,2cm, Walker Art Gallery, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 18:32(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustav Klimt, Ad&egrave;le Bloch-Bauer I, 1907, huile, argent et or sur toile, 138x138cm, Neue Galerie, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 19:45(4) &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Cubism and Abstract Art, 1936, catalogue d&rsquo;exposition, couverture, The Museum of Modern Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; 21:39(4)&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL);
