(16, 'Photographie et peinture, I', 'La naissance de la photographie Du mépris à la reconnaissance', '<p class=\"font_8\"><span class=\"color_14\">Dans ce premier volet sur la photographie, on s\'attachera &agrave; retracer l\'histoire de la d&eacute;couverte des principes photographiques en France et en Angleterre, ainsi qu\'&agrave; d&eacute;tecter minutieusement son influence sur la peinture.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><span class=\"color_14\">En moins d\'une d&eacute;cade apr&egrave;s la divulgation du proc&eacute;d&eacute;, l\'art du portrait peint se vit concurrenc&eacute; par l\'artifice des photographes. Puis ce fut au tour des peintres paysagistes de s\'impr&eacute;gner de la visualit&eacute; de ce que l\'on appelait alors des \'impressions photographiques\'.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><span class=\"color_14\">L\'art de l\'&Eacute;cole de Fontainebleau, d\'Ingres, de Manet, et m&ecirc;me des Pr&eacute;rapha&eacute;lites fut model&eacute; par cette nouvelle visualit&eacute; concurrente, m&ecirc;me si d&eacute;cri&eacute;e.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'L\'impression photographique est une invention disruptive dans l\'histoire de la représentation. La modernité en peinture ne peut se comprendre sans tenir compte de cette révolution technologique.', '2024-10-12 02:16:00', '2024-11-09 02:14:24', 'videosonline/October2024/a6TRVDyjaqvC7PllwMpL.jpg', '#646464', 'videosonline/October2024/AXf7c9IeRCLDwllD1184.jpg', 'Photography and painting, I', 'The Birth of Photography From Contempt to Recognition', '<p>In this first part on photography, we will focus on tracing the history of the discovery of photographic principles in France and England, as well as on carefully detecting its influence on painting.</p>\r\n<p>In less than a decade after the disclosure of the process, the art of the painted portrait found itself competing with the artifice of photographers. Then it was the turn of landscape painters to become imbued with the visuality of what were then called \'photographic impressions\'.</p>\r\n<p>The art of the School of Fontainebleau, Ingres, Manet, and even the Pre-Raphaelites was shaped by this new, competing, even if decried, visuality.</p>', 'Photographic printing is a disruptive invention in the history of representation. Modernity in painting cannot be understood without taking into account this technological revolution.', '<p>Aaron Scharf,<em> Art and Photography</em>, The Pingouin Press, 1968</p>', '<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Honor&eacute; Daumier, Nadar &eacute;levant la Photographie &agrave; la hauteur de l\'Art, 1862, lithographie, 44,5x31,3 cm, publi&eacute; dans Le Boulevard, 25 mai 1862 &nbsp; &nbsp;0:29(1), &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Nic&eacute;phore Niepce, Point de vue du Gras, 1826-1827, h&eacute;liographie, plaque au bitume de Jud&eacute;e, 16,2x20,2cm, Harry Ransom Center de l&rsquo;Universit&eacute; du Texas, Austin, Etats-Unis &nbsp;5:11(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Raphael Gaillarde, Chambre noire de Nic&eacute;phore Niepce, photographie, Mus&eacute;e Nic&eacute;phore Ni&eacute;pce, Chalon-sur-Sa&ocirc;ne 9:15(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">L&eacute;onard Fran&ccedil;ois Berger, Portrait posthume de N.J Ni&eacute;pce, 1854, huile sur toile, Mus&eacute;e Nic&eacute;phore Ni&eacute;pce, Chalon-sur-Sa&ocirc;ne &nbsp; 3:24(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Baptiste Sabatier-Biot, Louis-Jacques-Mand&eacute; Daguerre, 1844, daguerr&eacute;otype, 9,1x6,9cm, George Eastman House International Museum of Photography and Film, Rochester, Etats-Unis &nbsp;6:12(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Louis Bisson, Auguste Bisson, Portrait de Balzac, 1842, daguerr&eacute;otype, 92mmx92mm, &nbsp;Maison de Balzac, Paris 9:46(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Washington, [Unidentified man with beard, half-length portrait, full face], 1854-1860, daguerr&eacute;otype, Library of Congress, Washington, Etats-Unis &nbsp;10:32(1) ou 10:55(1)&iquest;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Edward Anthony, Case Factory. Covering and Finishing Room (Fabrique de bo&icirc;tes), 1854, The Isenburg Collection, Toronto, Canada 11:09(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Ichiki Shiro, Daguerr&eacute;otype de Shimazu Nariakira, 1857, daguerr&eacute;otype, Museum Shoko Shuseikan, Kagoshima, Japon 11:25(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Louis-Jacques-Mand&eacute; Daguerre, Triptyque de Munich (Boulevard du Temple), c.1839, daguerr&eacute;otype, d&eacute;truite, reproduction de c.1974, Bayerisches National Museum, Munich, Allemagne 12:11(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Baptiste-Louis Gros, Pont sur la Tamise &agrave; Londres, 1851, daguerr&eacute;otype, 15x20cm, Biblioth&egrave;que Nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; 13:15(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Plumbe, United States Capitol, Washington, D.C., east front elevation, c.1846, daguerr&eacute;otype, 12,7x17,8cm, Library of Congress, Washington, Etats-Unis &nbsp;13:23(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.getty.edu/art/collection/artists/2030/noel-marie-paymal-lerebours-french-1807-1873/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">N&ouml;el-Marie-Paymal Lerebours</a>, Syrie. Beyrouth, c.1842, gravure &agrave; l&rsquo;eau-forte r&eacute;alis&eacute;e &agrave; partir d&rsquo;un daguerr&eacute;otype, 15x20,3cm, dans&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.getty.edu/art/collection/artists/2030/noel-marie-paymal-lerebours-french-1807-1873/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">N&ouml;el-Marie-Paymal Lerebours</a>, Excursions daguerriennes. Vues et monuments les plus remarquables du globe, Paris &nbsp; 14:15(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.getty.edu/art/collection/artists/2030/noel-marie-paymal-lerebours-french-1807-1873/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">N&ouml;el-Marie-Paymal Lerebours</a>, Russie. &Eacute;glise de Vassili Blagennoi &agrave; Moscou, c.1842, gravure &agrave; l&rsquo;eau-forte r&eacute;alis&eacute;e &agrave; partir d&rsquo;un daguerr&eacute;otype, 15x20,3cm, dans&nbsp;<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"http://www.getty.edu/art/collection/artists/2030/noel-marie-paymal-lerebours-french-1807-1873/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">N&ouml;el-Marie-Paymal Lerebours</a>, Excursions d</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">aguerriennes. Vues et m</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">onuments l</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">es p</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lus r</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">emarquables du g</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">lobe, Paris &nbsp; 14:40(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">William Henry Fox Talbot, Feuille de foug&egrave;re \"Fern-Buckler\" sud am&eacute;ricaine, 1839, dessin photog&eacute;nique, non document&eacute; &nbsp;16:10(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Antoine Claudet, William Henry Fox Talbot, 1844, daguerr&eacute;otype, The British Library, Londres, Royaume-Uni 15:36(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">William Henry Fox Talbot, The Latticed Window (with the Camera oscura), c.1835, papier n&eacute;gatif, National Science and Media Museum, Bradford, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;17:00(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">George Wilson Bridges, Erechth&eacute;ion, Portique Ouest, c.1848, calotype n&eacute;gatif, 17x21,5cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp;18:16(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">George Wilson Bridges, Erechth&eacute;ion, Portique Ouest, c.1848, papier positif, 17x21,5cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp;18:16(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">William Henry Fox Talbot, Vues des boulevards de Paris, 1843, tirage sur papier sal&eacute; &agrave; partir de papier n&eacute;gatif, 16,4x21,4cm, Gilman Paper Company Collection, New York, Etats-Unis &nbsp; 18:21(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Benjamin Brecknell Turner, Ludlow, c.1852-1854, tirage sur papier albumin&eacute; &agrave; partir de papier n&eacute;gatif, Victoria and Albert Museum, Londres, Royaume-Uni &nbsp; 18:37(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Baptiste Camille Corot, Jeune m&egrave;re &agrave; l\'aur&eacute;e d\'un bois, 1856, clich&eacute; verre, 55,88x40,64cm, Los Angeles County Museum of Art, Los Angeles, Etats-Unis &nbsp;20:00(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Tigre en arr&ecirc;t, 1854, clich&eacute; verre, 16,8x20,2cm, Fogg Art Museums, Cambridge, Etats-Unis &nbsp;20:05(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Millet, La Pr&eacute;caution maternelle, c.1863, clich&eacute;-verre, 28,5x22,5cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 20:05(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean Garnier, [Portrait of an unidentified girl], c.1850, daguerr&eacute;otype coloris&eacute;, 21,3x16,8cm, &nbsp;Georges Eastman Museum, Rochester, Etats-Unis 20:33(1), 21:35(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Stillfried, Andersen , Takaboko Island, 1875-1885 , tirage coloris&eacute; d&