agrave; partir d\'un n&eacute;gatif papier cir&eacute; sec perdu, 20,6x15,6cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; 22:51(1)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Samuel Butler, Mr Heatherley\'s holiday: An Incident in Studio Life, 1874, huile sur toile, 9,21x7,08cm, Tate Britain, Londres, Royaume-Uni</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Samuel Butler, Rose the Model, c.1865, tirage &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine sur papier, 21x15,2cm, St. John&rsquo;s Coll&egrave;ge, Cambridge, Royaume-Uni</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Honor&eacute; Daumier, &laquo; -Tiens ma femme v&acute;la mon portrait en Daguerr&eacute;otype que je te rapporte de Paris. -Pourquoi donc est ce que tu n&acute;as pas aussi fait faire le mien pendant que tu y &eacute;tais&hellip;.&eacute;go&iuml;ste va! &raquo;, 1846, lithographie, planche n&ordm; 28, dans Les bons Bourgeois &nbsp; 0:50(2)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodor Hosemann, The