end of the family, publi&eacute; dans Punch&rsquo;s Almanack, 1855, Universit&auml;tsbibliothek Heidelberg, Heidelberg, Allemagne &nbsp; 3:38(2)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Interesting and valuable result., publi&eacute; dans Punch&rsquo;s Almanack, 1855, Universit&auml;tsbibliothek Heidelberg, Heidelberg, Allemagne &nbsp; 3:40(2)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Andr&eacute; Adolphe-Eug&egrave;ne Disd&eacute;ri, Chien posant, c.1865, planche de six cartes de visite, tirage &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s n&eacute;gatif verre au collodion, 20x24,7cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 4:38(2)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Andr&eacute;-Adolphe-Eug&egrave;ne Disd&eacute;ri, Portrait de Giuseppe Verdi, carte-de-visite, 8,4x5,2cm, Victoria and Albert Museum, Londres, Royaume-Uni 4:44(2)</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"fon