xui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix, 1854, planche III, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 5:21(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Homme nu assis de face, les jambes &eacute;cart&eacute;es, sur une peau de panth&egrave;re, 1854, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Durieu (planche XV), papier sal&eacute; d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s n&eacute;gatif papier,&nbsp; 17,8x12,8cm, Mus&eacute;e Bonnat-Helleu, Bayonne &nbsp; &nbsp; 5:37(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix,, 1854, planche V, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 5:41(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix, 1854, planche XIX, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 7:50(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix, 1854, planche XX, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 7:50(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, &Eacute;tude d&rsquo;homme nu, 1854, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Durieu, Mus&eacute;e Bonnat-Helleu, Bayonne &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eugène Delacroix, Trois &eacute;tudes d\'hommes, mine de plomb, 19,2x25,3cm, Musée des Beaux-Arts et d\'Archéologie de Besançon, &nbsp;Besançon &nbsp; 7:03(3), 7:41(3)?</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Homme nu debout de dos, tenant un bâton vertical, papier albuminé, 9,9x5,8cm, Collection Gérard Lévy, Musée du Louvre, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 6:58(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Homme nu assis sur une chaise, papier albuminé. 9,7x5,8cm, Collection Gérard Lévy, Musée du Louvre, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eugène Delacroix, &Eacute;tude de jambes d\'homme assis et &Eacute;tude d\'une tête, mine de plomb. 20,3x15,2cm, Musée des Beaux-Arts et d\'Archéologie de Besançon, &nbsp;Besançon &nbsp; 7:11(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, &laquo; Nu féminin assis sur un divan, la tête soutenue par un bras &raquo;, papier salé verni d\'après négatif papier, dans Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, [Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par [sic] Delacroix], 1854, planche XXIX, 14X9,5CM, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 7:59(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eugène Delacroix, Odalisque, 1857, huile sur bois, 39,5x31 cm, collection particulière&nbsp; &nbsp; 7:58(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Bonheur, Du b&eacute;tail par un lac, 1862, huile sur toile, 100,9x140,3cm, Dahesh Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; &nbsp; 11:36(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Victor Laisne, Portrait de Courbet &agrave; 34 ans, 1853, &eacute;preuve sur papier sal&eacute;, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s un n&eacute;gatif papier, 23,2x16,5cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:16(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Courbet &agrave; Sainte-P&eacute;lagie, 1871-1872, huile sur toile, 92x72cm, Mus&eacute;e Courbet, Ornans&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:29(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Adolphe Braun, Le Ch&acirc;teau de Chillon, 1867, photographie, Mus&eacute;e de l&rsquo;&Eacute;lys&eacute;e, Lausanne &nbsp; 16:44(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Le Ch&acirc;teau de Chillon, 1874-1877, huile sur toile, 73x92cm, &nbsp; &nbsp; 17:14(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Julien Vallou de Villeneuve, &Eacute;tudes d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s nature, nu, no. 1930, avant 1854, photographie, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 17:59(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, L\'Atelier du peintre. All&eacute;gorie r&eacute;elle d&eacute;terminant une phase de sept ann&eacute;es de ma vie artistique et morale, 1854-1855, d&eacute;tail, huile sur toile, 361x598cm, Mus&eacute;e d\'Orsay, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 18:07(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Julien Vallou de Villeneuve, &Eacute;tudes d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s nature, nu f&eacute;minin, no. 1940, 1853, papier sal&eacute; d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s n&eacute;gatif sur papier, invers&eacute;e, 12,2x16,4cm, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 18:18(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Femme au perroquet, 1866, huile sur toile, 129,5x195,6cm, Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, Etats-Unis &nbsp; &nbsp; 18:29(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Les Baigneuses, 1853, huile sur toile, 227x193cm, Mus&eacute;e Fabre, Montpellier&nbsp; &nbsp; 19:26(3), 20:59(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Corr&egrave;ge, Noli me tangere, c.15