illiam Elborne, Rodin devant La Porte de l\'Enfer se refl&eacute;tant dans un miroir, 1887, photographie, &nbsp; 13:41(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, Bas-relief d&eacute;di&eacute; &agrave; Maurice Rollinat, 1903,&nbsp; 15:46(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, La Porte de l\'Eenfer, 1881, troisi&egrave;me maquette, pl&acirc;tre, 115,5x5x30cm, Mus&eacute;e Rodin, Paris &nbsp; 15:57(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Lorenzo Ghiberti, La Porta del Paradiso, c.1425-1452, Battistero di Firenze, Florence, Italie &nbsp; 16:07(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, Le Baiser, c.1882, marbre, h.181,5cm, Mus&eacute;e Rodin, Paris&nbsp; 16:45(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, La Porte de l\'Enfer, c.1880-1890, bronze, 635x400x85cm, Mus&eacute;e Rodin, Paris &nbsp; 17:30(4), 17:45(4), 18:16(4), 19:39(4), 25:18(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Photo devant panth&eacute;on, Auguste Rodin, Le Penseur, 1903, bronze, h.180cm, Mus&eacute;e Rodin, Paris &nbsp; 20:56(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, La Porte de l\'Enfer, c.1880-1917, haut-relief en pl&acirc;tre, h.635cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; 24:38(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, La Porte de l\'Enfer, c.1880-1917, Philadelphia Museum of Art, Philadelphia, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 27:28(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Maurice Rollinat, 1888,&nbsp; 23:57(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, Petite T&ecirc;te coup&eacute;e de Saint Jean-Baptiste sur un plateau, c.1893, bronze, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 24:47(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Maurice Rollinat chantant au piano, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s une aquarelle in&eacute;dite de Gaston B&eacute;thune &raquo;, dans Octave Uzanne, L&rsquo;Art et l\'id&eacute;e, Ed. Ancienne Maison, Paris, 1892, p.193&nbsp; 25:09(4) &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Lorin dit Cabriol, &laquo; L\'Hydropathe Maurice Rollinat &raquo;, 1879, caricature, dans Les Hydropathes, no.8, 5 mai 1879 &nbsp; 24:05(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Uz&egrave;s, &laquo; Maurice Rollinat &raquo;,&nbsp; dans Le Chat noir, no.45, 18 novembre 1882&nbsp; 24:05(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, La Pens&eacute;e, c.1895, t&ecirc;te en marbre, h.74,2cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris&nbsp; 26:09(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', NULL);

